WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:08.368 --> 00:01:10.161 line:80%
-When did I ever ask--
-Stop that.

00:01:10.745 --> 00:01:13.415 line:80%
You didn't see a doctor
after what happened, did you?

00:01:17.544 --> 00:01:19.212 line:80%
[chuckles, scoffs]

00:01:19.296 --> 00:01:22.007 line:80%
Don't you think
I'd be quite the supportive wife?

00:01:23.967 --> 00:01:24.968 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:01:27.095 --> 00:01:28.305 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:01:37.188 --> 00:01:38.189 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:01:41.401 --> 00:01:42.485 line:80%
Stay still.

00:02:17.395 --> 00:02:18.563 line:80%
I saw a camera.

00:02:19.147 --> 00:02:20.148 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:02:20.732 --> 00:02:21.733 line:80%
Oh.

00:02:26.112 --> 00:02:28.156 line:80%
[stutters] Is it still there?

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:29.908 line:80%
[camera shutter clicking]

00:02:38.959 --> 00:02:40.418 line:80%
Should we try that again?

00:02:40.502 --> 00:02:42.629 line:80%
I think we can give them a better angle.

00:02:43.213 --> 00:02:44.214 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:02:45.048 --> 00:02:46.257 line:80%
Maybe like…

00:02:47.425 --> 00:02:48.426 line:80%
Mmm.

00:02:49.844 --> 00:02:51.513 line:80%
-Mmm.
-[clears throat]

00:02:52.973 --> 00:02:54.265 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-Mmm.

00:02:54.349 --> 00:02:55.350 line:80%
Now.

00:02:55.433 --> 00:02:57.185 line:80%
-Come on.
-[chuckles]

00:02:58.103 --> 00:03:00.438 line:80%
[shutter clicking]

00:03:00.522 --> 00:03:03.775 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:03:04.359 --> 00:03:06.277 line:20%
EPISODE 4

00:03:07.278 --> 00:03:09.030 line:20%
[court staff 1]
Did you see their kiss last night?

00:03:09.114 --> 00:03:10.740 line:20%
[court staff 2] They're totally in love.

00:03:10.824 --> 00:03:13.159 line:20%
-It kept me up all night.
-So romantic.

00:03:16.830 --> 00:03:17.872 line:20%
[Hyeon] Let's just go.

00:03:20.125 --> 00:03:21.626 line:20%
Announcing Grand Prince I-AN.

00:03:22.961 --> 00:03:24.421 line:20%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:03:39.269 --> 00:03:40.979 line:80%
LOVE ACROSS SOCIAL DIVIDES

00:03:41.062 --> 00:03:43.064 line:80%
LOVE DEFYING SOCIAL CLASS…

00:03:43.148 --> 00:03:44.733 line:80%
…I-AN AND SEONG'S MIDNIGHT TRYST

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:47.652 line:80%
[I-AN] We can no longer delay
an official statement.

00:03:48.403 --> 00:03:50.238 line:80%
This matter will cause public unrest.

00:03:50.739 --> 00:03:51.823 line:80%
We should be cautious--

00:03:51.906 --> 00:03:53.450 line:80%
Staying silent now

00:03:54.034 --> 00:03:55.535 line:80%
would only make things worse.

00:03:57.829 --> 00:03:59.372 line:80%
Are you hoping I deny it?

00:03:59.456 --> 00:04:01.374 line:80%
Your honor is at stake here.

00:04:01.458 --> 00:04:02.709 line:80%
A grand prince…

00:04:04.586 --> 00:04:07.088 line:80%
may kiss a woman and then
dismiss it as a mere dalliance?

00:04:07.589 --> 00:04:10.258 line:80%
Is this the honor
you wish for me to uphold?

00:04:10.341 --> 00:04:11.342 line:80%
That maiden

00:04:12.385 --> 00:04:14.846 line:80%
is a mere commoner of illegitimate birth.

00:04:14.929 --> 00:04:17.098 line:80%
[♪ music intensifies]

00:04:24.147 --> 00:04:25.440 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] Make it public.

00:04:29.110 --> 00:04:30.862 line:80%
[no audible dialogue]

00:04:32.864 --> 00:04:35.950 line:80%
As His Royal Highness stated,
this is a scandal by a grand prince.

00:04:36.576 --> 00:04:38.161 line:80%
We must do damage control.

00:04:38.244 --> 00:04:39.621 line:80%
"Damage control"?

00:04:40.205 --> 00:04:41.539 line:80%
With that in mind,

00:04:42.540 --> 00:04:43.666 line:80%
you should confirm it.

00:04:46.127 --> 00:04:47.378 line:80%
However,

00:04:47.462 --> 00:04:50.590 line:80%
you must state firmly
that there is no prospect of marriage.

00:04:51.508 --> 00:04:53.718 line:80%
Say that your acquaintance
has only just begun,

00:04:53.802 --> 00:04:55.261 line:80%
with no talk of marriage.

00:04:56.679 --> 00:04:59.182 line:80%
That should minimize any uncertainty.

00:04:59.265 --> 00:05:00.391 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:05:00.475 --> 00:05:03.436 line:80%
There's nothing unusual about a young pair
falling in and out of love.

00:05:03.520 --> 00:05:04.896 line:80%
If we treat it lightly,

00:05:05.730 --> 00:05:07.023 line:80%
it will remain that way.

00:05:07.107 --> 00:05:08.191 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:05:10.527 --> 00:05:11.528 line:80%
Let it be so.

00:05:11.611 --> 00:05:12.612 line:80%
However…

00:05:15.073 --> 00:05:17.492 line:80%
that maiden should move out
of your private residence.

00:05:17.575 --> 00:05:19.327 line:80%
-Why?
-Your Royal Highness!

00:05:19.410 --> 00:05:23.164 line:80%
Not only was she pelted with eggs
at her own home with private security,

00:05:23.248 --> 00:05:25.917 line:80%
but she is also bearing the brunt
of every insult online.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:27.293 line:80%
As if that were not enough,

00:05:28.002 --> 00:05:30.839 line:80%
she was photographed behind the palace,
under palace security.

00:05:31.339 --> 00:05:33.967 line:80%
If anything happens to her
because she was left alone,

00:05:34.884 --> 00:05:36.219 line:80%
will you answer for it?

00:05:41.850 --> 00:05:43.184 line:80%
We may end up parting ways,

00:05:44.686 --> 00:05:46.563 line:80%
or she may become my future wife.

00:05:48.314 --> 00:05:50.108 line:80%
Your Royal Highness, how could you…

00:05:50.191 --> 00:05:52.152 line:80%
My residence is already home to many.

00:05:55.530 --> 00:05:57.448 line:80%
<i>Attendants who maintain the grounds.</i>

00:05:58.908 --> 00:06:00.410 line:80%
<i>The Royal Guard for my safety.</i>

00:06:00.493 --> 00:06:01.494 line:80%
[cat meows]

00:06:01.578 --> 00:06:03.371 line:80%
<i>And there are even cats</i>
<i>that roam in my garden.</i>

00:06:05.039 --> 00:06:07.000 line:80%
The addition of my lady to that list…

00:06:09.627 --> 00:06:11.546 line:80%
will have little effect.

00:06:11.629 --> 00:06:12.755 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:06:15.675 --> 00:06:17.427 line:80%
Where will Your Royal Highness reside?

00:06:19.012 --> 00:06:22.432 line:80%
If Ms. Seong is permitted to stay
at your private residence for her safety,

00:06:22.932 --> 00:06:24.934 line:80%
then you must stay at the palace.

00:06:25.560 --> 00:06:27.645 line:80%
If rumors spread
that the palace is divided…

00:06:29.856 --> 00:06:31.232 line:80%
over a single woman,

00:06:32.317 --> 00:06:33.568 line:80%
it will be a grave matter.

00:06:41.201 --> 00:06:42.202 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:06:42.285 --> 00:06:44.746 line:80%
ROYAL SECRETARIAT:
OFFICIAL STATEMENT

00:06:44.829 --> 00:06:46.497 line:80%
This was approved? [gasps]

00:06:47.415 --> 00:06:49.584 line:80%
Is this how you chose
to handle the matter?

00:06:50.293 --> 00:06:54.130 line:80%
-You must compose yourself.
-How can I? [breathes heavily]

00:06:55.965 --> 00:06:58.843 line:80%
[exhales] Even if marriage is ruled out,

00:06:59.344 --> 00:07:02.388 line:80%
once the palace acknowledges them,
that woman will gain status.

00:07:03.097 --> 00:07:05.266 line:80%
Public interest is already at its peak.

00:07:05.350 --> 00:07:07.268 line:80%
Should he dare to include her
in state matters--

00:07:07.352 --> 00:07:08.603 line:80%
If you knew as much,

00:07:10.271 --> 00:07:11.898 line:80%
you should have exercised restraint.

00:07:14.067 --> 00:07:16.861 line:80%
Had you just left it alone,
the matter would've resolved itself.

00:07:16.945 --> 00:07:18.780 line:80%
Criticism was already pouring in.

00:07:18.863 --> 00:07:21.908 line:80%
"Failure to uphold the dignity
of his station and proper decorum."

00:07:21.991 --> 00:07:23.576 line:80%
They had plenty of grounds.

00:07:23.660 --> 00:07:24.869 line:80%
However,

00:07:25.870 --> 00:07:28.831 line:80%
because Your Majesty has opposed
the Grand Prince,

00:07:29.582 --> 00:07:31.793 line:80%
public opinion has shifted in his favor.

00:07:31.876 --> 00:07:35.797 line:80%
In fact, criticism of Your Majesty
has already begun to surface.

00:07:39.634 --> 00:07:40.927 line:80%
Just give your approval.

00:07:43.554 --> 00:07:46.057 line:80%
I will take care of the rest.

00:07:47.058 --> 00:07:49.352 line:80%
Do you have a plan?

00:07:51.437 --> 00:07:55.066 line:80%
There is no shortage of noblemen eager
to become the Prince's father-in-law,

00:07:55.149 --> 00:07:58.903 line:80%
and plenty in the business world are eager
to keep that woman in check as well.

00:08:02.615 --> 00:08:04.534 line:80%
That is to say,

00:08:05.410 --> 00:08:07.912 line:80%
should something happen,
it would hardly be a surprise.

00:08:12.417 --> 00:08:15.461 line:80%
[newsreader] <i>The Royal Secretariat</i>
<i>has just released an official statement.</i>

00:08:15.545 --> 00:08:18.172 line:80%
<i>In a royal first, the palace</i>
<i>has acknowledged a courtship</i>

00:08:18.256 --> 00:08:19.924 line:80%
<i>that isn't an engagement or marriage.</i>

00:08:20.008 --> 00:08:23.845 line:80%
<i>We'll discuss this with formal royal</i>
<i>spokesman, Professor Hwang Wookyeong.</i>

00:08:23.928 --> 00:08:26.639 line:80%
<i>-Welcome.</i>
<i>-Hello, it's nice to meet you.</i>

00:08:26.723 --> 00:08:29.642 line:80%
[newsreader]
<i>You have always maintained the stance…</i>

00:08:29.726 --> 00:08:30.727 line:80%
Hwang Wookyeong?

00:08:30.810 --> 00:08:32.437 line:80%
Don't you know who that is?

00:08:32.520 --> 00:08:35.982 line:80%
He used to be a royal spokesman
before he got blacklisted.

00:08:36.065 --> 00:08:38.818 line:80%
Come on, you must know him. Last year,

00:08:40.194 --> 00:08:41.654 line:80%
he was the one who claimed

00:08:41.738 --> 00:08:44.657 line:80%
the late king's death
wasn't an accident, but a murder.

00:08:44.741 --> 00:08:46.534 line:80%
[attendant]
A nut who jumps to conspiracy theories.

00:08:46.617 --> 00:08:47.702 line:80%
Be quiet.

00:08:47.785 --> 00:08:51.873 line:80%
<i>Many have noted that</i>
<i>this official statement is unprecedented.</i>

00:08:51.956 --> 00:08:52.957 line:80%
<i>What do you think?</i>

00:08:53.041 --> 00:08:55.793 line:20%
<i>I consider it to be</i>
<i>very befitting of the royal family.</i>

00:08:55.877 --> 00:08:59.547 line:80%
<i>Castle Group's Seong Huiju</i>
<i>is a commoner and businesswoman.</i>

00:08:59.630 --> 00:09:02.508 line:80%
<i>She is far from a traditional royal bride</i>
<i>by palace standards.</i>

00:09:02.592 --> 00:09:05.636 line:20%
<i>But it would've been difficult</i>
<i>for the palace to deny the relationship.</i>

00:09:05.720 --> 00:09:09.724 line:20%
<i>After all, there were</i>
<i>several definitive eyewitness accounts.</i>

00:09:10.433 --> 00:09:12.352 line:80%
[newsreader] <i>So are you suggesting that</i>

00:09:12.435 --> 00:09:14.479 line:80%
-<i>they had no choice but to recognize it?</i>
-[chuckles]

00:09:14.562 --> 00:09:16.689 line:80%
-[Wookyeong] <i>That's correct.</i>
-[newsreader] <i>Then Grand Prince I-AN…</i>

00:09:16.773 --> 00:09:17.774 line:80%
[I-AN] Seong Huiju.

00:09:17.857 --> 00:09:20.818 line:80%
[newsreader]
<i>…and what is the likelihood of marriage?</i>

00:09:20.902 --> 00:09:22.737 line:80%
[Wookyeong]
<i>Marriage would be highly unlikely.</i>

00:09:22.820 --> 00:09:25.573 line:20%
<i>Uh, I doubt the royal family</i>
<i>would accept a commoner,</i>

00:09:26.491 --> 00:09:28.951 line:20%
-<i>given their sensitivity about lineage.</i>
-[scoffs]

00:09:29.035 --> 00:09:32.580 line:80%
[newsreader] <i>Then how do you think</i>
<i>the royal family will proceed?</i>

00:09:33.122 --> 00:09:36.584 line:80%
[Wookyeong] <i>I don't expect them to provide</i>
<i>any further comments on the matter.</i>

00:09:36.667 --> 00:09:37.919 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:09:38.002 --> 00:09:39.587 line:80%
THE GRAND PRINCE CLIMBED
OVER A WALL

00:09:39.670 --> 00:09:41.798 line:80%
I knew this would happen.

00:09:42.548 --> 00:09:44.675 line:80%
I told you we should've tried again.

00:09:45.843 --> 00:09:47.220 line:80%
Well, I just…

00:09:47.303 --> 00:09:50.848 line:80%
-This angle is totally off. Darn it.
-[sighs]

00:09:50.932 --> 00:09:52.558 line:80%
What, are we in elementary school?

00:09:52.642 --> 00:09:54.977 line:80%
We look like toddlers smooching.

00:09:55.061 --> 00:09:56.938 line:80%
That's what you care about right now?

00:09:57.021 --> 00:09:58.689 line:80%
-We kissed and--
-Your Royal Highness.

00:09:59.190 --> 00:10:00.525 line:80%
Marketing only works

00:10:00.608 --> 00:10:04.529 line:80%
-when it's unbelievably sexy or shameless.
-[clears throat]

00:10:04.612 --> 00:10:05.655 line:80%
"Courtship"?

00:10:05.738 --> 00:10:08.658 line:80%
Wishy-washy words like that
will get us nowhere.

00:10:08.741 --> 00:10:10.118 line:80%
A tryst at a hotel!

00:10:10.618 --> 00:10:12.078 line:80%
That's sexy.

00:10:12.161 --> 00:10:13.955 line:80%
Prince I-AN's shotgun wedding!

00:10:15.164 --> 00:10:17.333 line:80%
That's shameless, right?

00:10:17.417 --> 00:10:20.962 line:80%
Doesn't it sound tempting, like junk food?

00:10:21.712 --> 00:10:22.713 line:80%
[sucks teeth]

00:10:24.590 --> 00:10:25.591 line:80%
[exhales]

00:10:28.094 --> 00:10:29.095 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:10:38.020 --> 00:10:39.021 line:80%
[♪ music stops]

00:10:39.105 --> 00:10:40.106 line:80%
[gulps]

00:10:40.690 --> 00:10:41.691 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:10:45.403 --> 00:10:48.531 line:80%
The quicker we get married,
the quicker we get divorced.

00:10:48.614 --> 00:10:50.616 line:80%
-Okay?
-[♪ gentle music continues]

00:10:54.203 --> 00:10:55.204 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:10:56.372 --> 00:10:57.540 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:10:57.623 --> 00:11:00.668 line:80%
Royal weddings are meant
to be conducted step by step…

00:11:00.751 --> 00:11:02.587 line:80%
Do you have that much time to waste?

00:11:02.670 --> 00:11:03.796 line:80%
[chuckling] I don't.

00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:05.047 line:80%
I mean…

00:11:05.131 --> 00:11:08.092 line:80%
Then what? Should we really make it
a shotgun wedding?

00:11:08.176 --> 00:11:10.219 line:80%
-So it's sexy and shameless?
-Yes.

00:11:10.303 --> 00:11:13.181 line:80%
When you pursue
a venture everyone opposes,

00:11:14.557 --> 00:11:17.143 line:80%
you can't give them time to object.

00:11:17.727 --> 00:11:19.061 line:80%
With that in mind…

00:11:21.439 --> 00:11:22.857 line:80%
Are you free now?

00:11:26.694 --> 00:11:29.113 line:80%
All of a sudden? Why do you ask?

00:11:35.244 --> 00:11:36.496 line:80%
I have a little time.

00:11:39.081 --> 00:11:40.625 line:80%
Can I take you somewhere?

00:11:42.210 --> 00:11:43.544 line:80%
Let's speed things up a bit.

00:11:47.131 --> 00:11:48.132 line:80%
Speed things up?

00:11:51.761 --> 00:11:52.803 line:80%
That's enough.

00:11:53.429 --> 00:11:56.098 line:80%
Do I look like a kindergartner to you?

00:11:57.016 --> 00:11:59.310 line:80%
-[grunts]
-Stay still.

00:11:59.393 --> 00:12:01.646 line:80%
Let's show them
what we're made of this time.

00:12:01.729 --> 00:12:05.566 line:80%
[grunts, smacks lips] Since when do people
show others up with their hair?

00:12:06.984 --> 00:12:10.404 line:80%
You were in sweats in those photos
where you were caught sucking face.

00:12:10.905 --> 00:12:14.534 line:80%
[sighs] They must be roasting His
Royal Highness for having terrible taste.

00:12:14.617 --> 00:12:15.993 line:80%
It makes me so upset.

00:12:16.077 --> 00:12:17.787 line:80%
What's wrong with his taste?

00:12:17.870 --> 00:12:21.457 line:80%
I mean, he chose me.
He clearly has exquisite taste.

00:12:21.541 --> 00:12:24.418 line:80%
And those sweats are super expensive.

00:12:24.502 --> 00:12:28.005 line:80%
[chuckles] Gosh. You must be a bird lover.

00:12:28.089 --> 00:12:30.633 line:80%
Just look at that magnificent bird's nest
on your head.

00:12:33.302 --> 00:12:36.389 line:80%
-[grunts] You did that on purpose. You…
-Stay still.

00:12:39.934 --> 00:12:42.812 line:80%
You really want me to clear your day?
All of it?

00:12:46.107 --> 00:12:49.569 line:80%
I'm just worried for your sake.
It'll make tomorrow brutal for you.

00:12:50.152 --> 00:12:51.320 line:80%
And for me too.

00:12:51.404 --> 00:12:53.447 line:80%
She wants to be Princess Diana.
What can I do?

00:12:54.073 --> 00:12:55.157 line:80%
Princess Diana?

00:12:55.241 --> 00:12:58.411 line:80%
As in Princess Diana from the UK? [laughs]

00:12:58.494 --> 00:12:59.495 line:80%
Jeez.

00:12:59.996 --> 00:13:02.999 line:80%
All this fuss will die down with time.

00:13:03.082 --> 00:13:06.085 line:80%
That's what the Queen Mother
is waiting for.

00:13:07.753 --> 00:13:09.171 line:80%
I won't let that happen.

00:13:11.757 --> 00:13:12.925 line:80%
[attendant] Your Royal Highness.

00:13:22.893 --> 00:13:24.061 line:80%
[♪ hopeful music plays]

00:13:51.047 --> 00:13:52.089 line:80%
Ta-da.

00:13:52.173 --> 00:13:54.634 line:80%
Isn't she stunning?
Like an angel come to life.

00:13:58.763 --> 00:14:00.306 line:80%
-Sure…
-[chuckles]

00:14:00.389 --> 00:14:01.849 line:80%
-…ly not.
-[♪ music ends]

00:14:02.475 --> 00:14:05.019 line:80%
You went for "spoiled princess"
and not an actual princess?

00:14:06.103 --> 00:14:07.104 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:14:08.105 --> 00:14:09.190 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[stammers]

00:14:11.025 --> 00:14:12.610 line:80%
[grunts] Is he for real?

00:14:12.693 --> 00:14:13.694 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:14:16.405 --> 00:14:18.491 line:80%
[Huiju] I told you this wasn't my vibe!

00:14:27.833 --> 00:14:28.834 line:80%
[whispers] I mean,

00:14:29.627 --> 00:14:32.046 line:80%
he's dressed in a princely suit.
What's his problem?

00:14:32.129 --> 00:14:34.090 line:80%
[whispers] That's what I'm saying, bro.

00:14:34.173 --> 00:14:35.299 line:80%
He is beyond difficult.

00:14:41.305 --> 00:14:42.515 line:80%
My goodness.

00:14:43.557 --> 00:14:44.558 line:80%
[grunts]

00:14:45.142 --> 00:14:46.519 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:15:05.204 --> 00:15:06.497 line:80%
Please give us a moment.

00:15:06.580 --> 00:15:08.207 line:80%
-I shall quickly fix this--
-No need.

00:15:34.358 --> 00:15:35.568 line:80%
Sorry about that.

00:15:43.075 --> 00:15:44.076 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:15:55.755 --> 00:15:57.465 line:80%
Thank you so much.

00:15:57.965 --> 00:15:59.133 line:80%
[I-AN clears throat]

00:16:02.720 --> 00:16:03.721 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:16:03.804 --> 00:16:07.641 line:80%
[sucks teeth] Perhaps a bit too plain?
[chuckles]

00:16:07.725 --> 00:16:08.976 line:80%
Really?

00:16:09.852 --> 00:16:11.145 line:80%
Hmm.

00:16:11.228 --> 00:16:12.897 line:80%
[smacks lips] I see what you mean.

00:16:13.522 --> 00:16:17.151 line:80%
He does look a bit dull and old-fashioned.

00:16:17.234 --> 00:16:18.527 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:16:20.362 --> 00:16:21.489 line:80%
-What the…
-[stutters]

00:16:22.782 --> 00:16:24.158 line:80%
-What are you doing?
-[chuckling] Seriously?

00:16:24.241 --> 00:16:25.701 line:80%
Are you feeling shy or something?

00:16:26.994 --> 00:16:28.662 line:80%
A royal never feels shy… Oh.

00:16:28.746 --> 00:16:30.080 line:80%
Just lose this.

00:16:30.164 --> 00:16:33.125 line:80%
Losing the pocket square
makes it a little bit less dull.

00:16:33.876 --> 00:16:34.919 line:80%
Better, right?

00:16:35.002 --> 00:16:38.756 line:80%
No, I was actually talking
about you, Ms. Seong.

00:16:39.256 --> 00:16:40.508 line:80%
-[Huiju] Oh.
-[chuckles]

00:16:40.591 --> 00:16:41.675 line:80%
Me?

00:16:42.259 --> 00:16:43.427 line:80%
That's not possible.

00:16:43.511 --> 00:16:45.262 line:80%
How could you ever call me plain?

00:16:46.722 --> 00:16:47.765 line:80%
[yelps]

00:16:48.641 --> 00:16:50.184 line:80%
[exhales]

00:16:51.101 --> 00:16:52.144 line:80%
I'm dazzling.

00:16:53.312 --> 00:16:54.438 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:16:57.066 --> 00:16:58.400 line:80%
So pretty.

00:17:01.904 --> 00:17:03.072 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:17:05.074 --> 00:17:06.534 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:17:19.547 --> 00:17:22.132 line:80%
-Go, Castle!
-[fans cheer]

00:17:22.216 --> 00:17:26.554 line:80%
-Let's go, Sharks!
-Let's go, Sharks!

00:17:26.637 --> 00:17:29.014 line:80%
-Come on, Sharks!
-Let's go!

00:17:29.098 --> 00:17:31.475 line:80%
[♪ Castle Sharks anthem playing]

00:17:34.144 --> 00:17:36.230 line:80%
It's not too late to call the Royal Guard.

00:17:37.273 --> 00:17:38.899 line:80%
We'd be better without them here.

00:17:39.984 --> 00:17:41.402 line:80%
[sighs, clears throat]

00:17:42.736 --> 00:17:43.737 line:80%
[Huiju] Your Royal Highness!

00:17:44.488 --> 00:17:45.489 line:80%
Ooh!

00:17:45.990 --> 00:17:46.991 line:80%
Here we go.

00:17:48.075 --> 00:17:49.535 line:80%
[sighs] Let's see here.

00:17:49.618 --> 00:17:50.995 line:80%
CASTLE SHARKS' LUCKY CHARM

00:17:51.579 --> 00:17:54.206 line:80%
Ooh, I have such a keen eye for detail.

00:17:54.290 --> 00:17:55.624 line:80%
You're 2XL, right?

00:17:56.166 --> 00:17:58.043 line:80%
If we wear matching outfits…

00:17:58.127 --> 00:18:00.504 line:80%
-He cannot.
-Why not?

00:18:00.588 --> 00:18:05.342 line:80%
His Royal Highness can't wear uniforms.
No expression of political views.

00:18:05.426 --> 00:18:07.720 line:80%
This isn't politics. It's just sports.

00:18:07.803 --> 00:18:10.347 line:80%
"A royal's private life
is never truly private,"

00:18:10.431 --> 00:18:11.682 line:80%
is the palace's position.

00:18:13.100 --> 00:18:14.101 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:18:16.020 --> 00:18:18.188 line:80%
Matching outfits would create some buzz.

00:18:19.815 --> 00:18:23.110 line:80%
-Then you can just wear it, Aide Choi.
-Really?

00:18:23.193 --> 00:18:26.238 line:80%
-It's so much more fun to cheer in this!
-So excited!

00:18:26.322 --> 00:18:27.448 line:80%
[cheers]

00:18:27.531 --> 00:18:30.326 line:80%
Your Royal Highness,
remember I have warm undertones?

00:18:30.409 --> 00:18:31.452 line:80%
This is perfect for me.

00:18:32.036 --> 00:18:33.662 line:80%
-Huh?
-You're not wearing this.

00:18:33.746 --> 00:18:35.205 line:80%
-Why not?
-Hmm?

00:18:40.419 --> 00:18:41.962 line:80%
[fans cheer]

00:18:45.507 --> 00:18:46.842 line:80%
[cheers]

00:18:47.593 --> 00:18:48.719 line:80%
[Taeju] Hey, you!

00:18:49.470 --> 00:18:51.513 line:80%
Why have you been ignoring my calls?

00:18:52.222 --> 00:18:53.223 line:80%
Why you little…

00:18:54.350 --> 00:18:55.351 line:80%
Oh, His Royal Highness?

00:18:56.185 --> 00:18:57.645 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:18:57.728 --> 00:18:59.605 line:80%
[stammers]
What brings you to such squalid grounds?

00:19:01.315 --> 00:19:02.900 line:80%
-Fried chicken?
-[chuckles]

00:19:02.983 --> 00:19:04.443 line:80%
You're getting ahead of yourself.

00:19:04.526 --> 00:19:07.821 line:80%
We don't speak until His Royal Highness
speaks to us first.

00:19:07.905 --> 00:19:09.031 line:80%
Oh!

00:19:09.698 --> 00:19:11.492 line:80%
Huiju has told me a lot about you.

00:19:12.076 --> 00:19:13.077 line:80%
About me?

00:19:13.160 --> 00:19:14.161 line:80%
[mouths word] What?

00:19:14.244 --> 00:19:16.747 line:80%
[mouthing words]
You better keep your trap shut.

00:19:17.456 --> 00:19:19.416 line:80%
[stutters] I wonder what she told you.

00:19:20.709 --> 00:19:21.877 line:80%
-Oh, right.
-[clears throat]

00:19:23.337 --> 00:19:24.463 line:80%
Yes.

00:19:25.589 --> 00:19:26.674 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:19:26.757 --> 00:19:29.927 line:80%
It is an honor to make your acquaintance,
Your Royal Highness.

00:19:30.010 --> 00:19:31.720 line:80%
I am Dayeong of the Han Family.

00:19:32.346 --> 00:19:33.389 line:80%
And your father's name?

00:19:33.472 --> 00:19:36.225 line:80%
He is Jeongseok of the Han family.

00:19:36.934 --> 00:19:38.435 line:80%
Former Minister of Justice.

00:19:39.603 --> 00:19:41.146 line:80%
What a commendable father you have.

00:19:41.981 --> 00:19:43.774 line:80%
[fans cheer]

00:19:46.694 --> 00:19:47.695 line:80%
Oh.

00:19:49.071 --> 00:19:50.781 line:80%
Jeongwoo's throwing the first pitch?

00:19:50.864 --> 00:19:52.408 line:80%
All right. Let's go!

00:19:52.491 --> 00:19:53.826 line:80%
[cheers]

00:19:55.577 --> 00:19:58.914 line:80%
[commentator 1] It appears we have Prime
Minister Min for the first pitch today.

00:19:58.998 --> 00:19:59.999 line:80%
[commentator 2] That's right.

00:20:00.082 --> 00:20:02.126 line:80%
He's famous for being
a hardcore fan of the Castle Sharks.

00:20:02.209 --> 00:20:06.755 line:80%
I hear he even dreamed of being
a baseball player when he was young.

00:20:06.839 --> 00:20:09.174 line:80%
I'm excited to see
how his first pitch will turn out.

00:20:15.180 --> 00:20:16.390 line:80%
[cheering]

00:20:16.473 --> 00:20:19.393 line:80%
[commentator 1] That was
a beautiful pitch. Do you hear that crowd?

00:20:19.476 --> 00:20:21.562 line:80%
The crowd is going wild for him.

00:20:21.645 --> 00:20:23.647 line:80%
The crowd's love for Prime Minister Min is

00:20:23.731 --> 00:20:25.983 line:80%
through the roof here
at Gocheok Sky Dome today.

00:20:26.066 --> 00:20:27.234 line:80%
[commentator 1] I couldn't agree more.

00:20:27.317 --> 00:20:28.902 line:80%
[cheering]

00:20:29.486 --> 00:20:30.863 line:80%
Min Jeongwoo!

00:20:32.197 --> 00:20:33.282 line:80%
[Huiju giggles]

00:20:38.579 --> 00:20:39.955 line:80%
[commentator 1] Up to bat is Gang Suho.

00:20:41.415 --> 00:20:43.667 line:80%
He pulled that one. It's high and deep.

00:20:43.751 --> 00:20:44.918 line:80%
Is it going over?

00:20:45.002 --> 00:20:46.336 line:80%
Over the wall and gone!

00:20:46.420 --> 00:20:48.797 line:80%
Gang Suho pulls off a comeback win!

00:20:48.881 --> 00:20:50.591 line:80%
[in English] Home run!

00:20:51.550 --> 00:20:52.634 line:80%
[in Korean] Nanny Jung!

00:20:53.260 --> 00:20:54.303 line:80%
You okay?

00:20:54.386 --> 00:20:56.805 line:80%
[commentator 2] <i>The Castle Sharks</i>
<i>are sinking their teeth in…</i>

00:20:56.889 --> 00:20:58.057 line:80%
Are you all right?

00:20:58.640 --> 00:20:59.767 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:20:59.850 --> 00:21:01.977 line:80%
I am fine, Your Majesty.

00:21:03.103 --> 00:21:05.105 line:80%
But the treat from Lord INPYEONG is…

00:21:05.898 --> 00:21:07.316 line:80%
No need for concern.

00:21:09.902 --> 00:21:11.028 line:80%
[blows]

00:21:11.111 --> 00:21:13.113 line:80%
The corndog is safe.

00:21:14.323 --> 00:21:16.158 line:80%
It certainly is not, Your Majesty!

00:21:16.658 --> 00:21:18.368 line:80%
[commentator 1]
<i>If we take a look, the stands are packed</i>

00:21:18.452 --> 00:21:19.953 line:80%
-<i>with fans in Castle Sharks jerseys…</i>
-[sighs]

00:21:22.247 --> 00:21:24.792 line:80%
[sucks teeth] Your Royal Highness.

00:21:25.375 --> 00:21:26.877 line:80%
-The Sharks…
-Stop it, babe.

00:21:26.960 --> 00:21:29.379 line:80%
-Get lost.
-[chuckles]

00:21:29.463 --> 00:21:31.507 line:80%
Let's go, Gang Suho!

00:21:31.590 --> 00:21:33.634 line:80%
You got this, Sharks!

00:21:35.427 --> 00:21:36.428 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:21:37.012 --> 00:21:38.013 line:80%
Jeongwoo.

00:21:38.806 --> 00:21:41.767 line:80%
You didn't leave after the first pitch?
I thought you'd already left.

00:21:42.351 --> 00:21:44.228 line:80%
My secretary said
not to waste the photo op.

00:21:44.311 --> 00:21:45.896 line:80%
Photo op? [gasps]

00:21:45.979 --> 00:21:47.439 line:20%
[fans cheer]

00:21:49.108 --> 00:21:50.609 line:20%
[buzzer sounds]

00:21:52.277 --> 00:21:53.862 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:21:53.946 --> 00:21:56.365 line:80%
Scooch over, Your Royal Highness.
Jeongwoo needs a seat.

00:22:00.202 --> 00:22:01.203 line:80%
Scooch over.

00:22:04.164 --> 00:22:05.332 line:80%
[Huiju] Come sit here, Jeongwoo.

00:22:10.796 --> 00:22:12.005 line:80%
You should have some too.

00:22:12.840 --> 00:22:13.924 line:80%
No, thank you.

00:22:14.007 --> 00:22:15.008 line:80%
You're not hungry?

00:22:16.093 --> 00:22:17.678 line:80%
-I am.
-Then eat.

00:22:18.846 --> 00:22:20.806 line:80%
[gasps] Are you a picky eater?

00:22:22.015 --> 00:22:24.643 line:80%
-It's not that…
-He can only eat at restaurants.

00:22:25.227 --> 00:22:26.353 line:80%
Why?

00:22:26.436 --> 00:22:28.897 line:80%
Because quality and safety
can't be guaranteed elsewhere.

00:22:29.398 --> 00:22:30.482 line:80%
And it's quite unseemly.

00:22:31.900 --> 00:22:32.901 line:80%
[huffs]

00:22:32.985 --> 00:22:34.319 line:80%
Am I expected to do that too?

00:22:34.820 --> 00:22:38.115 line:80%
-[fan 1] Kiss!
-[fans] Kiss!

00:22:38.198 --> 00:22:41.577 line:20%
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

00:22:41.660 --> 00:22:45.080 line:20%
[commentator 1] On the Kiss Cam,
we have the hottest couple of the moment.

00:22:45.164 --> 00:22:46.456 line:80%
-[commentator 2] That's right.
-It's them.

00:22:46.540 --> 00:22:47.541 line:80%
Oh, my gosh!

00:22:47.624 --> 00:22:49.376 line:80%
[commentator 1]
They really look great together.

00:22:49.459 --> 00:22:52.087 line:80%
But I'm sure it won't be easy
for His Royal Highness to kiss

00:22:52.171 --> 00:22:53.463 line:80%
-on the Kiss Cam.
-Right.

00:22:53.547 --> 00:22:55.465 line:80%
-Kiss!
-No! Stop!

00:22:55.549 --> 00:22:58.093 line:80%
-Kiss!
-No! They can't kiss!

00:22:58.177 --> 00:23:02.222 line:80%
-Kiss!
-No kiss! Where's the camera?

00:23:02.306 --> 00:23:05.184 line:80%
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

00:23:05.267 --> 00:23:08.478 line:80%
-Kiss!
-No! They can't kiss! No kiss!

00:23:08.562 --> 00:23:10.022 line:80%
No kiss!

00:23:10.105 --> 00:23:14.359 line:80%
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

00:23:14.443 --> 00:23:16.904 line:80%
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

00:23:16.987 --> 00:23:22.284 line:80%
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

00:23:22.367 --> 00:23:23.535 line:20%
MUST UPHOLD HIS DECORUM

00:23:23.619 --> 00:23:24.620 line:20%
[chuckles]

00:23:27.206 --> 00:23:28.207 line:20%
Sorry, we can't.

00:23:28.707 --> 00:23:29.708 line:20%
No, we can't!

00:23:30.250 --> 00:23:31.335 line:20%
[mouthing words] We can't kiss.

00:23:32.085 --> 00:23:33.503 line:80%
[cheering, clamoring]

00:23:40.719 --> 00:23:42.554 line:80%
[camera shutters clicking]

00:23:42.638 --> 00:23:43.805 line:80%
[Huiju giggles]

00:23:43.889 --> 00:23:44.890 line:80%
Hold on.

00:23:45.474 --> 00:23:48.769 line:80%
How are we supposed to be photographed
if they're covering us like this?

00:23:48.852 --> 00:23:49.853 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:23:50.604 --> 00:23:52.648 line:80%
-Huiju, let's go get dinner.
-Yeah?

00:23:52.731 --> 00:23:53.941 line:80%
We had corndogs already.

00:23:54.524 --> 00:23:55.984 line:80%
-That's not enough to fill you up.
-[scoffs]

00:23:56.526 --> 00:23:58.070 line:80%
Remember what you wanted last time?

00:23:58.820 --> 00:24:00.405 line:80%
-Last time?
-Yeah.

00:24:01.323 --> 00:24:03.867 line:80%
-Mmm. Oh, that!
-[scoffs]

00:24:03.951 --> 00:24:04.952 line:80%
[Huiju chuckles]

00:24:05.035 --> 00:24:06.036 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:24:07.079 --> 00:24:08.080 line:80%
Yes?

00:24:08.163 --> 00:24:09.164 line:80%
Back to the palace?

00:24:10.123 --> 00:24:11.833 line:80%
-What?
-Go on without me.

00:24:11.917 --> 00:24:13.418 line:80%
I'll have dinner with Jeongwoo.

00:24:13.502 --> 00:24:14.795 line:80%
I shall join you.

00:24:15.504 --> 00:24:16.505 line:80%
Pardon?

00:24:16.588 --> 00:24:19.967 line:80%
We came here together, so wouldn't it
be odd if we left separately?

00:24:20.926 --> 00:24:21.927 line:80%
Hmm.

00:24:22.886 --> 00:24:24.179 line:80%
[fans chattering]

00:24:28.308 --> 00:24:29.476 line:80%
[♪ amusing music playing]

00:24:30.811 --> 00:24:31.812 line:80%
Mmm.

00:24:37.943 --> 00:24:39.278 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:24:40.821 --> 00:24:42.531 line:80%
[squeals] Bye!

00:24:46.201 --> 00:24:47.202 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:25:00.716 --> 00:25:01.800 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:25:02.467 --> 00:25:03.635 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:25:05.304 --> 00:25:06.596 line:80%
Slow day at the office?

00:25:08.265 --> 00:25:09.349 line:80%
Pardon?

00:25:11.643 --> 00:25:12.811 line:80%
[♪ amusing music continues]

00:25:20.819 --> 00:25:22.362 line:80%
Mmm, it looks so good.

00:25:23.613 --> 00:25:24.698 line:80%
Please eat up.

00:25:28.618 --> 00:25:29.619 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:25:29.703 --> 00:25:32.080 line:80%
We can't eat before you take a bite.
Please, go ahead.

00:25:33.290 --> 00:25:35.000 line:80%
You should've gone back to the palace.

00:25:35.083 --> 00:25:37.919 line:80%
Hmm? What now? Is there another issue?

00:25:38.420 --> 00:25:40.172 line:80%
This is a restaurant, isn't it?

00:25:40.714 --> 00:25:41.798 line:80%
I know.

00:25:41.882 --> 00:25:43.675 line:80%
A royal shall never consume raw food.

00:25:43.759 --> 00:25:44.760 line:80%
It's the law.

00:25:45.927 --> 00:25:48.722 line:80%
Shall we order some gyeran-jjim
or doenjang soup for you?

00:25:49.306 --> 00:25:50.515 line:80%
-No need.
-Wait, hold on.

00:25:50.599 --> 00:25:52.684 line:80%
So, raw food? Nothing raw?

00:25:52.768 --> 00:25:55.520 line:80%
Not even beef tartare?
You can't have anything like that?

00:25:55.604 --> 00:25:57.773 line:80%
I cannot.
The risk of food poisoning is too high.

00:25:58.357 --> 00:25:59.358 line:80%
[grunts]

00:25:59.441 --> 00:26:00.567 line:80%
What a load of crap.

00:26:01.360 --> 00:26:02.361 line:80%
Load of…

00:26:03.487 --> 00:26:04.488 line:80%
[sighs]

00:26:04.571 --> 00:26:07.282 line:80%
-[whispers] A load of crap…
-You can't have street food.

00:26:07.366 --> 00:26:08.867 line:80%
Nothing raw either.

00:26:08.950 --> 00:26:11.244 line:80%
Where are you supposed
to find the joy in life?

00:26:12.037 --> 00:26:14.289 line:80%
That's why you shouldn't marry
His Royal Highness.

00:26:14.373 --> 00:26:15.457 line:80%
Too many restrictions.

00:26:16.750 --> 00:26:19.086 line:80%
What else? What else can't you do?

00:26:26.802 --> 00:26:28.887 line:80%
[imitating siren]

00:26:29.554 --> 00:26:30.555 line:80%
[screams]

00:26:30.639 --> 00:26:32.057 line:80%
[I-AN] Here I am.

00:26:33.433 --> 00:26:35.352 line:80%
[laughs]

00:26:35.435 --> 00:26:36.645 line:80%
Should we do this puzzle?

00:26:36.728 --> 00:26:39.940 line:80%
Hwan, may I try on your Dragon Robe?

00:26:40.023 --> 00:26:41.024 line:80%
Sure.

00:26:45.904 --> 00:26:46.905 line:80%
Let's see here.

00:26:48.532 --> 00:26:50.742 line:80%
Whoa, you look great in it.

00:26:50.826 --> 00:26:53.286 line:80%
-It looks good on me, right?
-Yeah.

00:26:54.538 --> 00:26:57.457 line:80%
Father, Hwan said I could…

00:27:01.211 --> 00:27:02.921 line:80%
How dare you mock

00:27:03.505 --> 00:27:05.966 line:80%
the Crown Prince's authority!

00:27:07.551 --> 00:27:08.802 line:80%
[sobbing]

00:27:12.055 --> 00:27:13.849 line:80%
[wailing]

00:27:18.395 --> 00:27:20.647 line:80%
[King] <i>Do not wear red.</i>

00:27:20.730 --> 00:27:22.065 line:80%
<i>That is the king's color.</i>

00:27:23.024 --> 00:27:24.359 line:80%
<i>Do not walk ahead.</i>

00:27:24.443 --> 00:27:25.944 line:80%
[wailing continues]

00:27:26.027 --> 00:27:27.487 line:80%
[King] <i>The king always leads.</i>

00:27:30.365 --> 00:27:32.701 line:80%
<i>Do not question anything.</i>

00:27:34.536 --> 00:27:36.121 line:80%
<i>It is the king's command.</i>

00:28:00.812 --> 00:28:02.063 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:28:03.231 --> 00:28:04.524 line:80%
Eat up while you still can.

00:28:05.775 --> 00:28:08.945 line:80%
You won't be able to
after the royal wedding.

00:28:11.406 --> 00:28:12.449 line:80%
[sighs]

00:28:13.742 --> 00:28:14.743 line:80%
Mmm.

00:28:16.495 --> 00:28:18.788 line:80%
[sucks teeth, exhales]

00:28:20.457 --> 00:28:23.251 line:80%
Mmm, so good. It's delicious.

00:28:25.921 --> 00:28:27.130 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:28:27.214 --> 00:28:28.965 line:80%
Were you at a raw fish restaurant?

00:28:29.466 --> 00:28:32.010 line:80%
-Do not worry. I did not eat any.
-And a baseball stadium?

00:28:32.093 --> 00:28:33.595 line:80%
Do not worry about that either.

00:28:33.678 --> 00:28:34.930 line:80%
No personal show of support.

00:28:35.013 --> 00:28:36.264 line:80%
No security issues.

00:28:36.348 --> 00:28:38.058 line:80%
It was unannounced, so no reporters.

00:28:38.642 --> 00:28:40.560 line:80%
You should have maintained decorum.

00:28:40.644 --> 00:28:41.978 line:80%
I did.

00:28:42.062 --> 00:28:44.814 line:80%
What is the use if you maintain it,
when she will not?

00:28:44.898 --> 00:28:46.608 line:80%
Because she has no reason to.

00:28:47.484 --> 00:28:49.444 line:80%
She is not a member
of the royal family yet.

00:28:49.528 --> 00:28:50.529 line:80%
[sighs]

00:28:50.612 --> 00:28:54.866 line:80%
Do you truly not see that her faults
will soon become your own?

00:28:55.450 --> 00:28:56.618 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:28:56.701 --> 00:28:59.162 line:80%
What on earth were you doing
while this unfolded?

00:29:03.333 --> 00:29:04.626 line:80%
We have no other choice.

00:29:05.126 --> 00:29:06.378 line:80%
I shall step in.

00:29:07.295 --> 00:29:08.296 line:80%
And do what?

00:29:08.380 --> 00:29:11.800 line:80%
Your Royal Highness cannot be
expected to know a woman's proprieties,

00:29:11.883 --> 00:29:15.512 line:80%
and it would be improper
for the Queen Mother to step forward.

00:29:16.179 --> 00:29:17.722 line:80%
That leaves only me, does it not?

00:29:18.473 --> 00:29:22.102 line:80%
I… am afraid I do not understand.

00:29:22.185 --> 00:29:23.186 line:80%
Please allow me

00:29:24.312 --> 00:29:25.981 line:80%
to discipline her.

00:29:27.941 --> 00:29:30.527 line:80%
[both whisper indistinctly]

00:29:32.362 --> 00:29:34.864 line:80%
Even palace attendants
who run wild like colts

00:29:34.948 --> 00:29:36.283 line:80%
become well-behaved

00:29:36.866 --> 00:29:38.535 line:80%
after I am done with them.

00:29:39.244 --> 00:29:40.829 line:80%
Rest assured, Your Royal Highness.

00:29:44.624 --> 00:29:45.625 line:80%
Goodness me.

00:29:46.418 --> 00:29:47.669 line:80%
[laughs]

00:29:47.752 --> 00:29:49.921 line:80%
Such excellent news. I am so relieved.

00:29:50.005 --> 00:29:52.632 line:80%
-I have full faith in you.
-[Hyeon laughing]

00:29:52.716 --> 00:29:54.593 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-[Hyeon] Such excellent news indeed.

00:29:54.676 --> 00:29:55.885 line:80%
[laughing, applauding]

00:30:01.433 --> 00:30:04.311 line:80%
Gosh, are you leaving already?
You need to have breakfast.

00:30:04.394 --> 00:30:06.229 line:80%
It's okay. I normally skip breakfast.

00:30:06.313 --> 00:30:07.897 line:80%
That simply will not do. Eat up.

00:30:07.981 --> 00:30:10.400 line:80%
Special apple bunnies for you. Open up.

00:30:11.151 --> 00:30:12.277 line:80%
There's some fuzz here.

00:30:12.861 --> 00:30:14.112 line:80%
-It's okay.
-Open up.

00:30:16.406 --> 00:30:17.407 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:30:17.490 --> 00:30:19.326 line:80%
We can skip all this next time--

00:30:19.409 --> 00:30:21.161 line:80%
-Have a lovely day.
-Have a lovely day.

00:30:22.579 --> 00:30:23.580 line:80%
Hmm.

00:30:24.914 --> 00:30:25.915 line:80%
Mmm.

00:30:32.005 --> 00:30:33.173 line:80%
[♪ combative music plays]

00:30:56.529 --> 00:30:58.448 line:80%
Oh, right. We met at the palace last time.

00:30:58.531 --> 00:31:00.575 line:80%
I am Jinsook of the Choi Family.

00:31:00.659 --> 00:31:02.911 line:80%
Feel free to address me
as Court Lady Choi.

00:31:03.495 --> 00:31:04.621 line:80%
Court Lady Choi.

00:31:05.330 --> 00:31:06.581 line:80%
Where are my manners?

00:31:09.793 --> 00:31:10.794 line:80%
I am Seong Huiju.

00:31:11.795 --> 00:31:13.755 line:80%
I am the head court lady
of Anhwadang Hall,

00:31:13.838 --> 00:31:15.340 line:80%
-the residence of the Grand Prince…
-[phone rings]

00:31:21.930 --> 00:31:23.139 line:80%
Hey, Ms. Do.

00:31:24.933 --> 00:31:27.769 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-Of course, I'm on my way.

00:31:29.688 --> 00:31:31.356 line:80%
Yes, I swear I'm on my way.

00:31:31.856 --> 00:31:34.609 line:80%
I can see Umyeonsan Tunnel up ahead.

00:31:37.070 --> 00:31:38.613 line:80%
I'm almost there.

00:31:38.697 --> 00:31:40.448 line:80%
I see you, Ms. Do.

00:31:40.949 --> 00:31:42.242 line:80%
I'm not lying!

00:31:43.368 --> 00:31:44.411 line:80%
So?

00:31:44.953 --> 00:31:46.663 line:80%
You just got in the car and left?

00:31:46.746 --> 00:31:49.040 line:80%
Yes. Was it something urgent?

00:31:50.667 --> 00:31:52.711 line:80%
Court Lady Choi must be irritated.

00:31:54.254 --> 00:31:55.547 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Why?</i>

00:31:58.758 --> 00:32:01.428 line:80%
She has been biding her time to teach you.

00:32:03.430 --> 00:32:05.056 line:80%
What exactly would she teach me?

00:32:05.140 --> 00:32:08.977 line:80%
The overall protocols, history,
and hierarchy of the royal family.

00:32:09.060 --> 00:32:10.270 line:80%
Things like that.

00:32:18.737 --> 00:32:19.863 line:80%
Good morning, Ms…

00:32:20.739 --> 00:32:22.615 line:80%
That sounds like a waste of time.

00:32:23.825 --> 00:32:25.785 line:80%
<i>Fine. I'll take the lessons.</i>

00:32:26.327 --> 00:32:27.912 line:80%
-<i>I need to go. Bye.</i>
-[chuckles]

00:32:32.876 --> 00:32:33.877 line:80%
[laughs]

00:32:34.669 --> 00:32:35.670 line:80%
[in English] Wow.

00:32:37.756 --> 00:32:40.508 line:80%
[in Korean] Are you sure
you two weren't close in school?

00:32:43.011 --> 00:32:44.345 line:80%
What? Why?

00:32:44.846 --> 00:32:46.014 line:80%
It's just that

00:32:46.556 --> 00:32:48.391 line:80%
you two make such a cute couple.

00:32:49.476 --> 00:32:50.685 line:80%
[laughs]

00:32:52.061 --> 00:32:53.855 line:80%
[clears throat, sniffles]

00:32:54.355 --> 00:32:55.356 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:32:57.776 --> 00:32:58.777 line:80%
Cute couple, my foot.

00:33:01.613 --> 00:33:04.032 line:80%
What? There's a lot to do today.

00:33:04.657 --> 00:33:06.117 line:80%
You have a lot of meetings too.

00:33:06.201 --> 00:33:07.744 line:80%
You couldn't trim it down a bit?

00:33:07.827 --> 00:33:09.621 line:80%
I did. I trimmed a lot.

00:33:09.704 --> 00:33:10.705 line:80%
[sighs]

00:33:10.789 --> 00:33:12.957 line:80%
Fine, let's hear it. Keep it very brief.

00:33:13.041 --> 00:33:16.836 line:80%
First off, you have a new product testing
with the R&amp;D manager in one hour.

00:33:16.920 --> 00:33:18.379 line:80%
You have one hour to do that.

00:33:18.463 --> 00:33:19.464 line:80%
One hour?

00:33:19.964 --> 00:33:21.591 line:80%
-For a new product testing?
-Yes.

00:33:22.091 --> 00:33:25.136 line:80%
You have lunch with Gang Taehyun
from Castle Pharma at 1:00.

00:33:25.220 --> 00:33:26.221 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:33:26.846 --> 00:33:28.515 line:80%
Why would he have lunch with me?

00:33:28.598 --> 00:33:29.808 line:80%
Isn't he in Taeju's circle?

00:33:29.891 --> 00:33:31.518 line:80%
He joined yours as of yesterday.

00:33:31.601 --> 00:33:33.853 line:80%
[scoffs] All of a sudden?

00:33:33.937 --> 00:33:35.522 line:80%
Didn't you also kiss the Grand Prince

00:33:35.605 --> 00:33:37.357 line:80%
-all of a sudden?
-[chokes]

00:33:38.316 --> 00:33:39.317 line:80%
[grunts]

00:33:40.068 --> 00:33:42.278 line:80%
[coughing]

00:33:44.906 --> 00:33:45.949 line:80%
Was he good?

00:33:46.032 --> 00:33:47.033 line:80%
What?

00:33:47.116 --> 00:33:50.078 line:80%
I mean, the cheeks were flushed.
Totally blushing for real.

00:33:50.161 --> 00:33:51.162 line:80%
[chuckling] Hey, come on.

00:33:51.955 --> 00:33:54.624 line:80%
[stammers] I was really hot that night.

00:33:54.707 --> 00:33:56.668 line:80%
That outfit is surprisingly warm.

00:33:58.378 --> 00:33:59.754 line:80%
Not you.

00:34:00.421 --> 00:34:01.589 line:80%
His Royal Highness.

00:34:02.423 --> 00:34:03.508 line:80%
What?

00:34:04.175 --> 00:34:05.844 line:80%
[chuckling] Did you get all fluttery too?

00:34:06.344 --> 00:34:07.345 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:34:08.513 --> 00:34:09.556 line:80%
Listen, Ms. Do.

00:34:10.056 --> 00:34:11.558 line:80%
Do I look like a teenager to you?

00:34:11.641 --> 00:34:15.728 line:80%
Why would I blush and get all fluttery
over a measly kiss?

00:34:15.812 --> 00:34:16.855 line:80%
Don't make me laugh.

00:34:16.938 --> 00:34:19.357 line:80%
I see. Not so great, huh?

00:34:19.858 --> 00:34:21.860 line:80%
Then again, he has no dating experience.

00:34:23.987 --> 00:34:26.698 line:80%
He has no dating experience?

00:34:26.781 --> 00:34:27.782 line:80%
Really?

00:34:28.366 --> 00:34:30.952 line:80%
He's never publicly dated anyone.
No tabloid rumors either.

00:34:31.536 --> 00:34:33.621 line:80%
[sighs] That's what you meant?

00:34:34.539 --> 00:34:35.790 line:80%
You may be wrong about that.

00:34:35.874 --> 00:34:36.875 line:80%
Hmm.

00:34:37.417 --> 00:34:39.002 line:80%
I guess he was surprisingly good.

00:34:39.085 --> 00:34:40.712 line:80%
Yeah, he clearly knew his way around…

00:34:41.421 --> 00:34:43.882 line:80%
Hey. That's not what I meant!

00:34:43.965 --> 00:34:45.133 line:80%
[laughs]

00:34:46.009 --> 00:34:48.011 line:80%
I'm not sure what you meant, but I got it.

00:34:48.094 --> 00:34:49.762 line:80%
Shall we get going now?

00:34:49.846 --> 00:34:51.180 line:80%
Why? What now?

00:34:51.264 --> 00:34:53.600 line:80%
We'll barely have enough time
for the tailor as it is.

00:34:53.683 --> 00:34:55.059 line:80%
New clothes?

00:34:55.143 --> 00:34:56.144 line:80%
For what?

00:34:56.811 --> 00:34:57.812 line:80%
Prime Minister Min did?

00:34:57.896 --> 00:34:59.147 line:80%
That's what I'm telling you.

00:34:59.647 --> 00:35:00.690 line:80%
It hasn't…

00:35:01.733 --> 00:35:03.568 line:80%
Could we have some privacy?

00:35:03.651 --> 00:35:04.861 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:35:07.405 --> 00:35:08.406 line:80%
[Taeju grunts]

00:35:10.283 --> 00:35:12.285 line:80%
It hasn't been made public yet,

00:35:12.368 --> 00:35:15.288 line:80%
but the PR team said
he invited Huiju to the roundtable.

00:35:15.371 --> 00:35:17.415 line:80%
But even Father was never invited to that.

00:35:17.498 --> 00:35:20.209 line:80%
Exactly! He threw money
and sucked up to them for an invite,

00:35:20.293 --> 00:35:23.129 line:80%
but they treated him like dirt
because he wasn't a noble.

00:35:23.212 --> 00:35:24.255 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:35:24.339 --> 00:35:26.799 line:80%
[chuckles]
Why would they invite Seong Huiju?

00:35:26.883 --> 00:35:30.553 line:80%
Babe, what would you hate more?
Huiju moving up in society

00:35:30.637 --> 00:35:32.472 line:80%
or becoming the heir to Castle Group?

00:35:33.264 --> 00:35:34.349 line:80%
I hate both equally.

00:35:34.432 --> 00:35:37.018 line:80%
But still, out of the two,
wouldn't the former be better?

00:35:37.101 --> 00:35:41.189 line:80%
Do you really want to see me bow down
and address her as Your Highness?

00:35:41.272 --> 00:35:43.942 line:80%
Babe, you need to step back
and see the bigger picture.

00:35:44.025 --> 00:35:47.320 line:80%
She doesn't become "Her Highness"
just because she marries him.

00:35:47.862 --> 00:35:50.073 line:80%
We may have to bow down a bit…

00:35:50.156 --> 00:35:51.157 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:35:51.240 --> 00:35:52.951 line:80%
-Hey, Han Dayeong. I--
-But!

00:35:53.534 --> 00:35:54.827 line:80%
She can't run a business.

00:35:54.911 --> 00:35:57.455 line:80%
Royals aren't allowed
to engage in economic activities.

00:35:58.957 --> 00:36:00.249 line:80%
No, I still don't like it.

00:36:00.333 --> 00:36:02.835 line:80%
What if she divorces him
after she becomes "Her Highness"?

00:36:03.711 --> 00:36:04.963 line:80%
Babe.

00:36:05.046 --> 00:36:06.798 line:80%
Have you ever heard of a royal divorce?

00:36:08.967 --> 00:36:10.259 line:80%
I thought they could.

00:36:10.343 --> 00:36:11.427 line:80%
If that were true,

00:36:11.511 --> 00:36:14.263 line:80%
Grand Prince I-AN
should've ascended the throne.

00:36:14.347 --> 00:36:16.391 line:80%
Wouldn't that have made more sense?

00:36:17.809 --> 00:36:18.810 line:80%
Maybe you're right.

00:36:19.519 --> 00:36:22.605 line:80%
-Babe, we should get a gift for Huiju.
-What?

00:36:22.689 --> 00:36:25.358 line:80%
We'll back her up
and get her married off to the Crown

00:36:25.441 --> 00:36:27.527 line:80%
so you can claim
Castle Group all for yourself.

00:36:31.280 --> 00:36:33.324 line:80%
[sighs] I don't know.

00:36:35.952 --> 00:36:36.953 line:80%
Come on now.

00:36:38.705 --> 00:36:39.956 line:80%
Who does Taeju belong to?

00:36:40.623 --> 00:36:41.624 line:80%
To Dayeong.

00:36:42.834 --> 00:36:44.752 line:80%
Who does Castle Group belong to?

00:36:47.922 --> 00:36:48.923 line:80%
To me.

00:36:49.007 --> 00:36:50.633 line:80%
[♪ sinister music playing]

00:36:57.557 --> 00:36:58.558 line:80%
[♪ music ends]

00:37:03.479 --> 00:37:04.647 line:80%
[sighs]

00:37:08.818 --> 00:37:10.278 line:80%
You stopped driving it around?

00:37:11.362 --> 00:37:13.573 line:80%
-What?
-The red open-top car.

00:37:13.656 --> 00:37:14.824 line:80%
[Huiju] Mmm.

00:37:15.366 --> 00:37:16.451 line:80%
Huh?

00:37:16.993 --> 00:37:18.411 line:80%
Did the Prince tell you to stop?

00:37:18.494 --> 00:37:19.662 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:37:19.746 --> 00:37:21.706 line:80%
As if I would ever listen.

00:37:22.957 --> 00:37:24.375 line:80%
It's in the shop.

00:37:24.459 --> 00:37:26.294 line:80%
They have a pick-up
and drop-off service now.

00:37:27.170 --> 00:37:28.296 line:80%
It broke down?

00:37:28.838 --> 00:37:30.256 line:80%
But you just got that car.

00:37:30.339 --> 00:37:33.259 line:80%
Yeah. Someone hit the bumper and ran.

00:37:33.342 --> 00:37:34.343 line:80%
Who?

00:37:34.427 --> 00:37:35.762 line:80%
How would I know?

00:37:37.055 --> 00:37:38.056 line:80%
But then again,

00:37:38.931 --> 00:37:41.434 line:80%
there are a lot of people
who'd like to crash my car.

00:37:52.487 --> 00:37:54.197 line:80%
I'm back.

00:37:56.157 --> 00:37:57.492 line:80%
Her Ladyship is here.

00:37:57.575 --> 00:37:59.744 line:80%
-Let me help you.
-Your Ladyship!

00:37:59.827 --> 00:38:01.621 line:80%
-I'll take that.
-No, I can carry them.

00:38:01.704 --> 00:38:02.872 line:80%
Just let me.

00:38:02.955 --> 00:38:05.333 line:80%
-Did you go shopping?
-Yeah. I can put those away.

00:38:05.416 --> 00:38:06.584 line:80%
Did you have dinner?

00:38:07.460 --> 00:38:08.836 line:80%
I had a light salad.

00:38:08.920 --> 00:38:10.296 line:80%
Get Her Ladyship dinner first.

00:38:10.379 --> 00:38:11.547 line:80%
-No, it's okay.
-Sure.

00:38:11.631 --> 00:38:14.175 line:80%
-We made sujeonggwa earlier--
-You are late.

00:38:24.477 --> 00:38:25.520 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:38:26.687 --> 00:38:28.231 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:38:30.274 --> 00:38:31.526 line:80%
I know it is late,

00:38:32.151 --> 00:38:34.362 line:80%
but your royal education
cannot be delayed.

00:38:35.446 --> 00:38:36.823 line:80%
I ask for your understanding.

00:38:38.574 --> 00:38:40.368 line:80%
Yes, of course.

00:38:40.451 --> 00:38:43.037 line:80%
I understand.
I understand indeed. [chuckles]

00:38:44.831 --> 00:38:46.624 line:80%
Do not repeat yourself.

00:38:46.707 --> 00:38:48.167 line:80%
It makes you look frivolous.

00:38:49.127 --> 00:38:50.294 line:80%
Okay.

00:38:51.462 --> 00:38:53.339 line:80%
Dragging out the ends of your words

00:38:54.006 --> 00:38:55.091 line:80%
is also forbidden.

00:38:56.634 --> 00:38:57.677 line:80%
Yep.

00:38:58.553 --> 00:39:01.681 line:80%
Your education will be comprehensive.

00:39:01.764 --> 00:39:06.227 line:80%
For your public role, you will learn
royal protocol, royal history,

00:39:06.310 --> 00:39:09.147 line:80%
proper conduct, and the court hierarchy.

00:39:09.647 --> 00:39:10.648 line:80%
For your private role,

00:39:10.731 --> 00:39:13.568 line:80%
you will learn who to meet
and whom to avoid.

00:39:13.651 --> 00:39:15.069 line:80%
What to say…

00:39:16.779 --> 00:39:19.407 line:80%
and what not to say.

00:39:19.490 --> 00:39:21.701 line:80%
Let us start with your posture.

00:39:32.086 --> 00:39:33.880 line:80%
Your standing posture

00:39:35.131 --> 00:39:36.257 line:80%
is good.

00:39:37.550 --> 00:39:38.551 line:80%
Please walk.

00:39:39.302 --> 00:39:40.303 line:80%
Up to there.

00:39:41.179 --> 00:39:42.263 line:80%
Mmm.

00:39:48.019 --> 00:39:49.228 line:80%
More energy.

00:39:52.565 --> 00:39:53.608 line:80%
[vocalizes]

00:39:57.361 --> 00:39:59.071 line:80%
[whimpers]

00:40:01.616 --> 00:40:02.658 line:80%
Stand up straight.

00:40:06.787 --> 00:40:09.373 line:80%
Can you not even stand still?

00:40:22.637 --> 00:40:24.222 line:80%
Though you are small in stature,

00:40:24.722 --> 00:40:26.224 line:80%
do not bow your head.

00:40:27.308 --> 00:40:29.227 line:80%
Posture is dignity.

00:40:29.310 --> 00:40:30.895 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:40:31.896 --> 00:40:34.357 line:80%
Yes, Queen Mother.

00:40:37.985 --> 00:40:40.947 line:80%
No, that is not right.

00:40:41.030 --> 00:40:42.073 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:40:42.740 --> 00:40:44.450 line:80%
Let me show you one last time.

00:40:44.533 --> 00:40:45.826 line:80%
Watch carefully.

00:40:49.038 --> 00:40:51.207 line:80%
Like this.

00:40:51.290 --> 00:40:54.001 line:80%
Extend your leg.

00:40:54.085 --> 00:40:55.211 line:80%
Extend…

00:40:55.795 --> 00:40:57.004 line:80%
Oh, dear.

00:40:58.881 --> 00:41:00.174 line:80%
Right here.

00:41:00.258 --> 00:41:02.718 line:80%
-It hurts right here, doesn't it?
-Yes, it does.

00:41:02.802 --> 00:41:04.762 line:80%
You have so many knots here.

00:41:05.346 --> 00:41:07.265 line:80%
This must hurt a lot.

00:41:07.348 --> 00:41:08.808 line:80%
-Yes, a bit.
-Here too.

00:41:08.891 --> 00:41:11.060 line:80%
-Does this hurt even more?
-That is right.

00:41:11.143 --> 00:41:13.062 line:80%
Oh, my goodness.

00:41:13.938 --> 00:41:16.941 line:80%
I've been doing Pilates for ten years,

00:41:17.024 --> 00:41:19.527 line:80%
so I can just tell from someone's posture.

00:41:20.403 --> 00:41:23.948 line:80%
-Now is not the time for this…
-No, now is exactly the right time.

00:41:24.031 --> 00:41:25.658 line:80%
Let's try that once more.

00:41:25.741 --> 00:41:27.326 line:80%
-All right.
-I'll help you.

00:41:27.410 --> 00:41:30.496 line:80%
-Like this?
-There you go. Lift your leg and…

00:41:30.579 --> 00:41:31.914 line:80%
Good.

00:41:31.998 --> 00:41:33.332 line:80%
[I-AN] You said to leave it to you.

00:41:34.083 --> 00:41:35.543 line:80%
Is this how you discipline?

00:41:36.210 --> 00:41:37.420 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:41:37.962 --> 00:41:39.630 line:80%
[♪ emotional ballad playing]

00:41:53.477 --> 00:41:55.271 line:80%
-[♪ music stops]
-[both gasp]

00:42:02.236 --> 00:42:03.237 line:80%
Hey.

00:42:04.113 --> 00:42:05.448 line:80%
We have a lot of eyes on us.

00:42:06.532 --> 00:42:08.367 line:80%
Please take her away.

00:42:09.577 --> 00:42:10.661 line:80%
What?

00:42:11.579 --> 00:42:13.539 line:80%
Do you know how much work I have to do?

00:42:13.622 --> 00:42:16.667 line:80%
Must I devote my whole night
to posture correction? [chuckles]

00:42:18.085 --> 00:42:19.295 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:42:19.378 --> 00:42:20.921 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness.

00:42:23.257 --> 00:42:24.258 line:80%
[grunts]

00:42:26.260 --> 00:42:28.554 line:80%
What brings you to your private residence?

00:42:29.764 --> 00:42:31.682 line:80%
I have been away from it for far too long.

00:42:32.350 --> 00:42:35.394 line:80%
And I was curious to see
how your royal lessons were progressing.

00:42:35.478 --> 00:42:36.812 line:80%
Please make your return.

00:42:36.896 --> 00:42:38.439 line:80%
The palace gates will soon be shut.

00:42:43.611 --> 00:42:44.695 line:80%
[sighs]

00:42:46.030 --> 00:42:47.698 line:80%
-You should come with me.
-Pardon?

00:42:47.782 --> 00:42:50.034 line:80%
Your primary duty
is to protect Anhwadang Hall,

00:42:50.618 --> 00:42:52.161 line:80%
not discipline her. Is that not so?

00:42:52.661 --> 00:42:54.747 line:80%
-But Your Royal Highness--
-Do not argue.

00:42:54.830 --> 00:42:55.915 line:80%
It is my command.

00:42:58.417 --> 00:42:59.460 line:80%
[sighs]

00:43:04.715 --> 00:43:05.758 line:80%
[I-AN clears throat]

00:43:20.398 --> 00:43:22.024 line:80%
With the Ancestral Rite concluded,

00:43:22.525 --> 00:43:24.485 line:80%
we will begin planning the overseas tour.

00:43:30.950 --> 00:43:32.159 line:80%
How many stops this year?

00:43:34.537 --> 00:43:36.163 line:80%
It should be similar to last year.

00:43:40.876 --> 00:43:43.003 line:80%
Why? Shall I reduce them?

00:43:43.587 --> 00:43:44.755 line:80%
Won't you stop me?

00:43:46.882 --> 00:43:48.134 line:80%
-What?
-My marriage.

00:43:49.343 --> 00:43:50.845 line:80%
I thought you'd try at least once.

00:43:50.928 --> 00:43:52.012 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:43:53.431 --> 00:43:54.473 line:80%
I am not you.

00:44:07.278 --> 00:44:09.613 line:80%
You may be able to decide something

00:44:09.697 --> 00:44:12.616 line:80%
simply based on whether you find
something agreeable or not.

00:44:14.034 --> 00:44:15.369 line:80%
But if I do that…

00:44:26.255 --> 00:44:27.715 line:80%
the country would collapse.

00:44:28.299 --> 00:44:29.717 line:80%
Checkmate.

00:44:33.262 --> 00:44:34.680 line:80%
I'd rather you yelled at me.

00:44:41.061 --> 00:44:42.646 line:80%
I handled the Junghwajeon incident.

00:44:45.149 --> 00:44:47.985 line:80%
The Queen Mother should no longer
take issue with it either.

00:44:56.243 --> 00:44:57.995 line:80%
In a royal funeral,

00:44:58.829 --> 00:45:02.791 line:80%
the body is cleansed and an ablution
is performed at the Place of Passing,

00:45:03.501 --> 00:45:06.545 line:80%
along with the ritual wailing,
the fencing, mouth-filling,

00:45:06.629 --> 00:45:08.631 line:80%
and ice-bedding ceremonies.

00:45:08.714 --> 00:45:11.759 line:80%
-The Royal Ancestral Altar--
-They really do all that?

00:45:12.968 --> 00:45:16.138 line:80%
It is discourteous to interrupt.

00:45:16.722 --> 00:45:19.099 line:80%
My apologies. I was just really curious.

00:45:19.725 --> 00:45:22.311 line:80%
Did they do all that three years ago too?

00:45:22.978 --> 00:45:24.146 line:80%
That is correct.

00:45:24.980 --> 00:45:26.398 line:80%
Why don't I remember it at all?

00:45:27.900 --> 00:45:31.195 line:80%
The last public funeral ceremony
held by the royal family

00:45:31.737 --> 00:45:33.531 line:80%
was in 2005.

00:45:34.240 --> 00:45:35.241 line:80%
Why?

00:45:37.493 --> 00:45:40.829 line:80%
<i>The mother of the Grand Prince,</i>
<i>Queen UIHYEON,</i>

00:45:41.622 --> 00:45:43.707 line:80%
<i>passed away 20 years ago,</i>

00:45:43.791 --> 00:45:46.377 line:80%
<i>in the fourth lunar month</i>
<i>of the Eulyu year.</i>

00:45:52.841 --> 00:45:56.929 line:80%
<i>His father, King HUIJONG,</i>
<i>passed away seven years later,</i>

00:45:57.012 --> 00:46:00.599 line:80%
<i>in the sixth month of the Imjin year.</i>

00:46:04.979 --> 00:46:06.730 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:46:09.858 --> 00:46:11.443 line:80%
[wailing]

00:46:11.527 --> 00:46:13.362 line:80%
[Lady Choi] <i>And just three years ago,</i>

00:46:13.445 --> 00:46:15.364 line:80%
<i>His Majesty's father</i>

00:46:15.948 --> 00:46:20.119 line:80%
<i>and Grand Prince I-AN's older brother,</i>
<i>King SEONJONG, passed away.</i>

00:46:26.417 --> 00:46:28.168 line:80%
<i>With tragedies so frequent,</i>

00:46:28.794 --> 00:46:31.338 line:80%
<i>the royal family decided</i>
<i>to keep the ceremony private.</i>

00:46:31.422 --> 00:46:33.424 line:80%
[sobbing]

00:46:35.050 --> 00:46:36.051 line:80%
Your Ladyship?

00:46:36.135 --> 00:46:37.595 line:80%
It's just all too much.

00:46:37.678 --> 00:46:39.763 line:80%
-Pardon?
-It's no wonder

00:46:40.389 --> 00:46:42.891 line:80%
His Royal Highness
has a chip on his shoulder.

00:46:43.392 --> 00:46:45.102 line:80%
I mean, I knew all about it,

00:46:46.478 --> 00:46:48.397 line:80%
but to hear about it one after the other…

00:46:53.027 --> 00:46:54.153 line:80%
Don't mind me.

00:46:55.988 --> 00:46:57.781 line:80%
I just want to be alone right now.

00:47:10.419 --> 00:47:11.754 line:80%
QUEEN UIHYEON PASSED AWAY…

00:47:11.837 --> 00:47:13.130 line:80%
"Queen UIHYEON

00:47:13.839 --> 00:47:16.050 line:80%
passed away
in a vehicle rollover accident."

00:47:18.427 --> 00:47:19.470 line:80%
KING HUIJONG PASSED…

00:47:19.553 --> 00:47:21.930 line:80%
"King HUIJONG passed away
after a heart attack."

00:47:22.806 --> 00:47:24.683 line:80%
"Could it have been prevented?"

00:47:28.771 --> 00:47:32.650 line:80%
"King SEONJONG
tragically met his death in a fire."

00:47:42.910 --> 00:47:44.495 line:80%
And if he suffers indigestion?

00:47:44.578 --> 00:47:45.871 line:80%
You would be wholly to blame.

00:47:45.954 --> 00:47:47.581 line:80%
And if Queen Mother is angered?

00:47:49.208 --> 00:47:51.335 line:80%
Is that why he was so on edge back then?

00:48:00.177 --> 00:48:02.471 line:80%
PRINCE

00:48:03.639 --> 00:48:04.807 line:80%
[line ringing]

00:48:14.274 --> 00:48:15.317 line:80%
Is he working?

00:48:24.410 --> 00:48:25.619 line:80%
Please introduce yourself.

00:48:26.495 --> 00:48:29.164 line:80%
She has been
my closest companion recently.

00:48:31.834 --> 00:48:33.836 line:80%
I am Jaegyeong of the Kim Family,

00:48:34.336 --> 00:48:35.671 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:48:36.672 --> 00:48:40.342 line:80%
There is a dinner
with the royal correspondents tomorrow.

00:48:41.510 --> 00:48:44.430 line:80%
I cannot accompany you due to my illness.

00:48:44.513 --> 00:48:45.681 line:80%
Take her in my stead.

00:48:46.807 --> 00:48:49.017 line:80%
Her father is
the proprietor of Jeongui Daily.

00:48:49.601 --> 00:48:51.186 line:80%
She will be able to aid you.

00:48:55.315 --> 00:48:58.569 line:80%
You have been falling ill
quite frequently lately.

00:48:58.652 --> 00:49:01.238 line:80%
Perhaps because I have had
a lot on my mind.

00:49:03.824 --> 00:49:04.992 line:80%
Court Lady Im, approach.

00:49:07.578 --> 00:49:09.079 line:80%
What is Her Majesty's ailment?

00:49:09.663 --> 00:49:10.664 line:80%
Pardon?

00:49:11.623 --> 00:49:13.041 line:80%
She has been ill for a few days.

00:49:13.667 --> 00:49:15.753 line:80%
The royal physician must have visited.

00:49:15.836 --> 00:49:17.880 line:80%
What is Her Majesty's ailment?

00:49:23.343 --> 00:49:24.970 line:80%
You have failed in your duties.

00:49:25.512 --> 00:49:26.930 line:80%
Not at all, Your Royal Highness.

00:49:29.224 --> 00:49:31.101 line:80%
Instruct the royal physician

00:49:31.185 --> 00:49:34.188 line:80%
to monitor Her Majesty's condition
three times a day.

00:49:34.772 --> 00:49:38.442 line:80%
The illness may spread,
so private audiences must be forbidden.

00:49:39.109 --> 00:49:40.444 line:80%
That includes Lord INPYEONG…

00:49:42.905 --> 00:49:44.531 line:80%
and most certainly, His Majesty.

00:49:53.290 --> 00:49:55.167 line:80%
You are unwell,
so you should get some rest.

00:49:55.751 --> 00:49:58.545 line:80%
I shall attend the engagement alone.

00:50:04.593 --> 00:50:06.178 line:80%
I feel terrible.

00:50:06.261 --> 00:50:08.847 line:80%
It appears I have upset
His Royal Highness.

00:50:09.890 --> 00:50:11.016 line:80%
Do not be troubled.

00:50:12.684 --> 00:50:14.645 line:80%
Hunting inherently requires

00:50:15.813 --> 00:50:17.481 line:80%
patience above all.

00:50:36.333 --> 00:50:37.501 line:80%
[sighs]

00:50:38.836 --> 00:50:40.587 line:80%
That woman by the Queen Mother's side.

00:50:41.255 --> 00:50:43.507 line:80%
Conduct a comprehensive
background check on her.

00:50:43.590 --> 00:50:44.591 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:50:45.384 --> 00:50:46.385 line:80%
No.

00:50:47.928 --> 00:50:49.179 line:80%
Start with Jeongui Daily.

00:50:49.263 --> 00:50:50.597 line:80%
Look into them first.

00:50:50.681 --> 00:50:52.140 line:80%
Understood, sir.

00:50:56.436 --> 00:50:57.437 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:50:57.980 --> 00:51:00.065 line:80%
You have a missed call from Ms. Seong.

00:51:00.148 --> 00:51:01.149 line:80%
Several, actually.

00:51:09.825 --> 00:51:11.118 line:80%
[sighs]

00:51:14.121 --> 00:51:16.290 line:80%
THREE MISSED CALLS
JUNIOR ALUM

00:51:21.128 --> 00:51:22.462 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:51:27.342 --> 00:51:28.343 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:51:28.427 --> 00:51:30.262 line:80%
<i>What do you need? I'm busy.</i>

00:51:30.762 --> 00:51:32.681 line:80%
Uh, I'm also really…

00:51:38.478 --> 00:51:39.771 line:80%
Let's not get angry.

00:51:40.355 --> 00:51:42.649 line:80%
You must take pity on this poor soul.

00:51:46.320 --> 00:51:47.321 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:51:47.905 --> 00:51:50.282 line:80%
<i>I'm only going to say this once,</i>
<i>so listen carefully.</i>

00:51:51.658 --> 00:51:52.826 line:80%
I'm on your side.

00:51:57.789 --> 00:52:02.127 line:80%
What I mean is, I can only succeed
if you succeed as well.

00:52:02.794 --> 00:52:05.505 line:80%
Husband and wife stand as one, right?

00:52:06.256 --> 00:52:09.801 line:80%
<i>I'm not saying this</i>
<i>because I adore you or anything,</i>

00:52:09.885 --> 00:52:11.178 line:80%
<i>so don't get too excited.</i>

00:52:14.723 --> 00:52:15.933 line:80%
Are you still there?

00:52:16.850 --> 00:52:17.976 line:80%
Hello?

00:52:19.645 --> 00:52:20.687 line:80%
Your Royal Highness?

00:52:21.355 --> 00:52:22.356 line:80%
[line clicks]

00:52:22.439 --> 00:52:23.440 line:80%
Did he hang up?

00:52:23.982 --> 00:52:25.025 line:80%
Oh, he did.

00:52:26.735 --> 00:52:27.736 line:80%
Cool.

00:52:29.571 --> 00:52:30.864 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:52:31.907 --> 00:52:33.075 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:52:33.158 --> 00:52:35.160 line:80%
JUNIOR ALUM

00:52:39.998 --> 00:52:41.208 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:52:47.965 --> 00:52:49.716 line:80%
-Choi Hyeon.
-Yes, Your Royal Highness?

00:52:53.303 --> 00:52:54.846 line:80%
I made sure to run over.

00:52:54.930 --> 00:52:56.390 line:80%
Did someone ask you to?

00:52:57.557 --> 00:52:58.684 line:80%
Pardon?

00:52:58.767 --> 00:53:00.560 line:80%
I will head to my private residence
in the evening.

00:53:01.395 --> 00:53:04.815 line:80%
Uh, but Prime Minister Min
requested you stay in the palace…

00:53:05.607 --> 00:53:09.736 line:80%
But where did he come up
with such nonsense? [chuckles]

00:53:10.487 --> 00:53:12.072 line:80%
I shall prepare accordingly.

00:53:15.993 --> 00:53:17.285 line:80%
[sighs]

00:53:18.161 --> 00:53:19.246 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:53:21.456 --> 00:53:22.833 line:80%
[children chattering]

00:53:25.210 --> 00:53:27.379 line:80%
-To the internet café!
-Remember last time…

00:53:30.882 --> 00:53:32.426 line:80%
Your Majesty!

00:53:33.427 --> 00:53:35.595 line:80%
-Are you all right, Your Majesty?
-Yeah.

00:53:36.096 --> 00:53:37.639 line:80%
Behave yourself before His Majesty!

00:53:38.348 --> 00:53:39.808 line:80%
My apologies, Your Majesty.

00:53:47.399 --> 00:53:48.650 line:80%
You should be more careful.

00:53:48.734 --> 00:53:50.819 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty. Please get back safely.

00:53:52.070 --> 00:53:53.280 line:80%
-Hey.
-Wait for me.

00:53:54.489 --> 00:53:55.532 line:80%
This way, Your Majesty.

00:54:01.705 --> 00:54:04.207 line:80%
What are you doing here,
Prime Minister Min?

00:54:04.291 --> 00:54:07.002 line:80%
Today is not Sunday.

00:54:08.503 --> 00:54:09.755 line:80%
I am aware, Your Majesty.

00:54:10.255 --> 00:54:13.133 line:80%
Unfortunately, I must deal
with an urgent matter this weekend.

00:54:13.216 --> 00:54:16.595 line:80%
I am afraid I must cancel
this Sunday's history lesson.

00:54:16.678 --> 00:54:18.638 line:80%
Official duties must take priority.

00:54:18.722 --> 00:54:19.723 line:80%
Instead,

00:54:20.390 --> 00:54:21.641 line:80%
we will have a lesson today.

00:54:22.476 --> 00:54:25.479 line:80%
Or we could just skip it.

00:54:31.276 --> 00:54:32.319 line:80%
Come this way!

00:54:42.788 --> 00:54:44.289 line:80%
I wish I could play.

00:54:54.424 --> 00:54:55.467 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:54:56.676 --> 00:54:57.677 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty?

00:54:58.261 --> 00:55:00.013 line:80%
I would like to make a request.

00:55:04.476 --> 00:55:08.480 line:80%
[Lady Choi, in English]
One, two, three, four.

00:55:08.563 --> 00:55:11.650 line:80%
Five, six, seven.

00:55:11.733 --> 00:55:13.652 line:80%
[in Korean] We keep a smile on our face.

00:55:13.735 --> 00:55:16.029 line:80%
Smile. With elegance.

00:55:16.113 --> 00:55:17.155 line:80%
There you go.

00:55:17.239 --> 00:55:19.908 line:80%
[in English] One, two, three…
[in Korean] Straighten your back!

00:55:21.910 --> 00:55:23.829 line:80%
-Again!
-Again. Go.

00:55:24.371 --> 00:55:25.664 line:80%
[Lady Choi sighs]

00:55:31.128 --> 00:55:35.632 line:80%
We once again steady our breathing,
while maintaining a smile on our face.

00:55:36.133 --> 00:55:39.052 line:80%
-[in English] One, two, three, four.
-[chuckles]

00:55:39.136 --> 00:55:44.099 line:80%
-Five, six, seven, eight.
-At this rate, she'll break all the china.

00:55:44.182 --> 00:55:46.643 line:80%
I know, right? They're not cheap, either.

00:55:47.144 --> 00:55:49.312 line:80%
But does that even help?

00:55:49.813 --> 00:55:51.565 line:80%
I've seen it in period dramas before.

00:55:51.648 --> 00:55:53.775 line:80%
-Put your arms down.
-I doubt it.

00:55:53.859 --> 00:55:55.193 line:80%
Smile!

00:55:56.111 --> 00:55:57.237 line:80%
Smile!

00:55:57.320 --> 00:55:59.030 line:80%
There you go, with elegance.

00:55:59.823 --> 00:56:02.284 line:80%
[in English] Six, seven, eight!

00:56:02.367 --> 00:56:05.495 line:80%
One, two, three, four.

00:56:05.579 --> 00:56:08.540 line:80%
Five, six, seven, eight.

00:56:08.623 --> 00:56:09.958 line:80%
-[in Korean] Your Majesty!
-There--

00:56:10.917 --> 00:56:11.960 line:80%
Hello, Your Maje…

00:56:16.840 --> 00:56:18.175 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:56:21.136 --> 00:56:22.220 line:80%
So you're saying

00:56:22.846 --> 00:56:24.347 line:80%
you basically played hooky?

00:56:24.431 --> 00:56:25.599 line:80%
How dare you!

00:56:25.682 --> 00:56:28.393 line:80%
I am here to see Uncle.

00:56:28.894 --> 00:56:30.604 line:80%
Did you make an appointment?

00:56:32.189 --> 00:56:35.650 line:80%
Well… No, I did not.

00:56:35.734 --> 00:56:37.110 line:80%
Exactly.

00:56:37.194 --> 00:56:39.821 line:80%
You showed up
without even making an appointment.

00:56:39.905 --> 00:56:41.406 line:80%
To play with your uncle.

00:56:42.032 --> 00:56:43.575 line:80%
That's what playing hooky is.

00:56:45.493 --> 00:56:46.661 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:56:47.746 --> 00:56:48.747 line:80%
Well done.

00:56:49.831 --> 00:56:51.124 line:80%
You only live once.

00:56:51.208 --> 00:56:52.918 line:80%
You should play hooky at least once.

00:56:53.960 --> 00:56:55.128 line:80%
Shall we?

00:57:02.761 --> 00:57:03.929 line:80%
What do you want to do?

00:57:04.804 --> 00:57:07.974 line:80%
He has been a bit overwhelmed recently.

00:57:09.017 --> 00:57:10.644 line:80%
He's still young.

00:57:11.937 --> 00:57:14.231 line:80%
If only there were
an age limit for being king.

00:57:15.190 --> 00:57:16.191 line:80%
It's too bad.

00:57:18.652 --> 00:57:20.111 line:80%
[stammers] Yes…

00:57:23.531 --> 00:57:24.532 line:80%
Sorry.

00:57:25.033 --> 00:57:27.535 line:80%
My husband just wouldn't let me go.

00:57:27.619 --> 00:57:31.081 line:80%
Hmm. You two dated for years,
and you still like each other?

00:57:31.164 --> 00:57:33.541 line:80%
Of course. I like him more every day.

00:57:33.625 --> 00:57:35.293 line:80%
He gets more handsome every day.

00:57:35.377 --> 00:57:37.295 line:80%
And he treats me
better and better every day.

00:57:37.379 --> 00:57:38.546 line:80%
[all chuckle]

00:57:39.381 --> 00:57:42.592 line:80%
As you should.
You abandoned your family to marry him.

00:57:43.385 --> 00:57:44.427 line:80%
What?

00:57:45.470 --> 00:57:49.516 line:80%
I mean, everyone knows you made
your father collapse when you got married.

00:57:49.599 --> 00:57:52.727 line:80%
He threatened to disown you
and ban you from using the Han name.

00:57:53.228 --> 00:57:54.229 line:80%
It caused quite a stir.

00:57:54.312 --> 00:57:55.563 line:80%
Stop that.

00:57:55.647 --> 00:57:57.816 line:80%
Nobody talks like that anymore.

00:57:57.899 --> 00:57:59.192 line:80%
Oh, please.

00:57:59.276 --> 00:58:02.612 line:80%
Everyone still judges people by status
and pedigree behind closed doors.

00:58:02.696 --> 00:58:04.030 line:80%
We're just jealous.

00:58:04.531 --> 00:58:07.117 line:80%
People like us would never dream of
marrying for love.

00:58:07.200 --> 00:58:08.326 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:58:09.160 --> 00:58:11.538 line:80%
I guess you have no idea
what's happening in the world

00:58:11.621 --> 00:58:13.873 line:80%
because you're always cooped up
in your chambers.

00:58:13.957 --> 00:58:16.584 line:80%
My sister-in-law, with her lowly pedigree,

00:58:16.668 --> 00:58:18.628 line:80%
is dating the Grand Prince.

00:58:19.254 --> 00:58:20.505 line:80%
Haven't you heard?

00:58:21.631 --> 00:58:22.632 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:58:24.092 --> 00:58:25.593 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:58:27.304 --> 00:58:28.513 line:80%
-[screams]
-What's wrong?

00:58:28.596 --> 00:58:29.723 line:80%
That witch!

00:58:30.598 --> 00:58:32.851 line:80%
Kim Jaegyeong was like that in school too.

00:58:32.934 --> 00:58:34.519 line:80%
She's just so nasty.

00:58:34.602 --> 00:58:37.272 line:80%
Maybe I should've just dragged her
out of there by her hair.

00:58:38.148 --> 00:58:39.733 line:80%
You should have.

00:58:39.816 --> 00:58:41.443 line:80%
What? Can I do that?

00:58:42.402 --> 00:58:43.737 line:80%
Why not?

00:58:43.820 --> 00:58:46.781 line:80%
Make sure you grab it next time.
I'll cover the settlement.

00:58:48.074 --> 00:58:49.826 line:80%
My sweet husband.

00:58:50.368 --> 00:58:53.413 line:80%
Of course. Money comes before dignity.

00:58:53.496 --> 00:58:54.914 line:80%
This is why you make money.

00:58:59.294 --> 00:59:01.880 line:80%
Here I go.

00:59:02.380 --> 00:59:03.423 line:80%
Done.

00:59:04.466 --> 00:59:05.550 line:80%
Good.

00:59:06.343 --> 00:59:07.344 line:80%
All right.

00:59:10.764 --> 00:59:11.806 line:80%
Now…

00:59:14.517 --> 00:59:16.978 line:80%
you get three chances to hit this pebble.

00:59:17.062 --> 00:59:18.688 line:80%
One, two, three.

00:59:18.772 --> 00:59:20.648 line:80%
If it lands inside this circle,

00:59:20.732 --> 00:59:22.525 line:80%
all this land becomes Your Majesty's.

00:59:22.609 --> 00:59:24.361 line:80%
-Easy, right?
-It is.

00:59:27.405 --> 00:59:28.406 line:80%
Jeongwoo!

00:59:32.994 --> 00:59:35.622 line:80%
Min Jeongwoo!

00:59:40.502 --> 00:59:41.628 line:80%
Yes? What do you need?

00:59:41.711 --> 00:59:42.962 line:80%
Jeongwoo…

00:59:44.923 --> 00:59:47.801 line:80%
Prime Minister Min,
you will be the referee.

00:59:48.426 --> 00:59:49.427 line:80%
Me?

00:59:49.511 --> 00:59:51.513 line:80%
The loser has to grant the winner's wish.

00:59:51.596 --> 00:59:53.932 line:80%
Rock, paper, scissors. [squeals]

00:59:54.015 --> 00:59:55.183 line:80%
I won.

00:59:55.934 --> 00:59:56.935 line:80%
Here we go.

00:59:57.018 --> 00:59:58.353 line:80%
That's one.

01:00:06.319 --> 01:00:09.030 line:80%
[all exclaiming, laughing]

01:00:14.244 --> 01:00:15.787 line:80%
-Got you!
-[exclaims]

01:00:15.870 --> 01:00:17.205 line:80%
-I got someone!
-My goodness!

01:00:17.288 --> 01:00:18.540 line:80%
[laughs]

01:00:20.708 --> 01:00:22.085 line:80%
[laughs]

01:00:22.168 --> 01:00:26.297 line:80%
Green light… Red light.

01:00:26.965 --> 01:00:28.383 line:80%
Youngseon, you moved.

01:00:28.883 --> 01:00:31.511 line:80%
Green light…

01:00:35.014 --> 01:00:37.684 line:80%
One, two, three.

01:00:37.767 --> 01:00:40.603 line:80%
-Four, five, six, seven.
-Five, six, seven.

01:00:40.687 --> 01:00:41.896 line:80%
-One, two.
-One, two.

01:00:41.980 --> 01:00:45.150 line:80%
-Four!
-Four, five!

01:00:45.692 --> 01:00:46.776 line:80%
One, two!

01:00:46.860 --> 01:00:49.279 line:80%
[cheering]

01:00:49.362 --> 01:00:50.697 line:80%
Well done, Your Majesty!

01:01:02.959 --> 01:01:04.127 line:80%
Wow!

01:01:04.210 --> 01:01:05.670 line:80%
I won!

01:01:07.755 --> 01:01:09.757 line:80%
I said I won!

01:01:12.135 --> 01:01:13.261 line:80%
[cheering]

01:01:16.556 --> 01:01:17.807 line:80%
You did not forget, right?

01:01:19.559 --> 01:01:20.560 line:80%
What?

01:01:20.643 --> 01:01:23.104 line:80%
You promised to grant me a wish.

01:01:24.105 --> 01:01:25.106 line:80%
I said that?

01:01:26.816 --> 01:01:29.444 line:80%
Are you a man of virtue or of profit?

01:01:30.695 --> 01:01:31.946 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:01:34.949 --> 01:01:36.034 line:80%
I remember.

01:01:42.499 --> 01:01:44.250 line:80%
This is your wish?

01:01:44.834 --> 01:01:46.252 line:80%
I saw it when I arrived.

01:01:46.961 --> 01:01:49.380 line:80%
I have always wanted
to ride one with the wings.

01:01:50.173 --> 01:01:51.549 line:80%
You cannot, Your Majesty.

01:01:51.633 --> 01:01:54.135 line:80%
It is not an approved vehicle.

01:01:54.219 --> 01:01:58.097 line:80%
But it is a car with wings!

01:01:58.181 --> 01:02:01.935 line:80%
It's the only one in the country!

01:02:02.018 --> 01:02:03.853 line:80%
Observing protocol is a matter of customs.

01:02:03.937 --> 01:02:07.065 line:80%
It is the duty of a man of virtue
to uphold propriety and decorum.

01:02:07.148 --> 01:02:08.483 line:80%
Have you forgotten?

01:02:21.079 --> 01:02:24.415 line:80%
Why are you all saying
I cannot do anything? Why?

01:02:25.208 --> 01:02:27.627 line:80%
I am the king!

01:02:27.710 --> 01:02:30.713 line:80%
-I should be able to do what I want!
-My goodness, Your Majesty.

01:02:30.797 --> 01:02:31.798 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>What did you just say?</i>

01:02:32.507 --> 01:02:35.760 line:80%
His Majesty is at your private residence
with Prime Minister Min.

01:02:36.970 --> 01:02:38.096 line:80%
What's he doing there?

01:02:38.179 --> 01:02:40.598 line:80%
How would I know? [chuckles]

01:02:41.391 --> 01:02:42.392 line:80%
[sighs]

01:02:42.892 --> 01:02:46.104 line:80%
You will be back
before the palace gates are shut, right?

01:02:47.438 --> 01:02:50.525 line:80%
Be sure to keep your eyes on the road.
Don't forget your seat belt.

01:02:52.402 --> 01:02:53.861 line:80%
Call me later, sir!

01:02:59.117 --> 01:03:00.368 line:80%
Hmm.

01:03:06.374 --> 01:03:08.710 line:80%
You must keep
the windows closed at all times.

01:03:08.793 --> 01:03:10.920 line:80%
Yes, I'll be sure to keep them closed.

01:03:13.756 --> 01:03:14.924 line:80%
Must you be the driver?

01:03:17.093 --> 01:03:19.596 line:80%
It's the only one in the country.

01:03:19.679 --> 01:03:22.974 line:80%
I don't want anyone else driving it.
[clears throat]

01:03:23.725 --> 01:03:24.726 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:03:25.476 --> 01:03:28.563 line:80%
I will be in the escort vehicle
ahead of you and clear the road.

01:03:28.646 --> 01:03:30.565 line:80%
You must not go above 60 km per hour.

01:03:30.648 --> 01:03:32.734 line:80%
And you must stay on the phone with me.

01:03:33.276 --> 01:03:34.485 line:80%
If, by any chance,

01:03:35.361 --> 01:03:37.530 line:80%
an unexpected situation arises…

01:03:38.114 --> 01:03:39.449 line:80%
Don't worry.

01:03:40.033 --> 01:03:43.161 line:80%
I will put His Majesty's safety
above all else.

01:03:43.244 --> 01:03:44.746 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:03:50.668 --> 01:03:53.129 line:80%
-And the rear security detail?
-Have them follow me.

01:03:53.212 --> 01:03:55.548 line:80%
-I will follow behind Ms. Seong's car.
-[door closes]

01:03:55.632 --> 01:03:57.216 line:80%
You will?

01:03:57.800 --> 01:04:01.512 line:80%
If security details surround her car,
people will assume it's a motorcade.

01:04:01.596 --> 01:04:03.181 line:80%
It might attract spectators.

01:04:03.264 --> 01:04:04.974 line:80%
If they discover His Majesty inside--

01:04:05.058 --> 01:04:06.392 line:80%
No, that cannot happen!

01:04:06.476 --> 01:04:07.810 line:80%
[gasps]

01:04:08.603 --> 01:04:10.104 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] May I borrow a car?

01:04:10.188 --> 01:04:11.606 line:80%
Something discreet.

01:04:36.214 --> 01:04:37.423 line:80%
[official] <i>Are there any issues?</i>

01:04:37.507 --> 01:04:39.509 line:80%
No, we're fine.

01:04:39.592 --> 01:04:41.678 line:80%
We're going too slow. That's the issue.

01:04:41.761 --> 01:04:43.763 line:80%
Can we not go any faster?

01:04:44.347 --> 01:04:45.431 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:04:55.358 --> 01:04:58.111 line:80%
-Let's go!
-[chuckles]

01:05:02.615 --> 01:05:03.991 line:80%
What's wrong with this?

01:05:11.833 --> 01:05:12.959 line:80%
[gasps] Your Majesty!

01:05:14.001 --> 01:05:15.002 line:80%
Damn it.

01:05:21.718 --> 01:05:23.386 line:80%
Your Majesty.

01:05:23.469 --> 01:05:25.430 line:80%
You have your seat belt on, right?

01:05:35.940 --> 01:05:37.775 line:80%
[horns honking]

01:05:39.861 --> 01:05:41.487 line:80%
Seong Huiju, what's wrong?

01:05:42.572 --> 01:05:43.698 line:80%
Jeongwoo!

01:05:44.282 --> 01:05:46.451 line:80%
-The brakes aren't working!
-[crying]

01:05:54.041 --> 01:05:56.043 line:80%
Your Majesty, close your window.

01:06:07.054 --> 01:06:09.265 line:80%
[horns honking]

01:06:14.312 --> 01:06:15.438 line:80%
[panting]

01:06:23.571 --> 01:06:24.697 line:80%
[breathing heavily]

01:06:26.282 --> 01:06:27.992 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[horn honks]

01:06:30.787 --> 01:06:32.371 line:80%
[horn honks]

01:06:35.666 --> 01:06:38.211 line:80%
-[yelps]
-[horn honks]

01:06:48.304 --> 01:06:49.305 line:80%
YANGSEO-GYO BRIDGE

01:06:53.851 --> 01:06:55.144 line:80%
[grunts]

01:07:12.119 --> 01:07:13.621 line:80%
[breathing heavily]

01:07:13.704 --> 01:07:15.498 line:80%
Hang on tight, Your Majesty.

01:07:16.624 --> 01:07:17.667 line:80%
[grunts]

01:07:52.577 --> 01:07:53.911 line:80%
[gasps]

01:07:53.995 --> 01:07:55.329 line:80%
[crying]

01:07:57.915 --> 01:07:58.916 line:80%
[crash]

01:08:11.137 --> 01:08:12.722 line:80%
[Huiju breathing heavily]

01:08:40.041 --> 01:08:42.001 line:80%
[♪ romantic music playing]

01:08:58.351 --> 01:08:59.644 line:80%
[gasps]

01:09:08.569 --> 01:09:11.489 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:09:48.109 --> 01:09:49.568 line:80%
You even hurt your face?

01:09:49.652 --> 01:09:51.445 line:80%
When that's all you have going for you?

01:09:51.529 --> 01:09:53.072 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Someone messed with your car.</i>

01:09:53.739 --> 01:09:54.782 line:80%
[Hyejeong] <i>Let's reconsider this.</i>

01:09:54.865 --> 01:09:56.033 line:80%
This marriage.

01:09:56.117 --> 01:09:59.286 line:80%
<i>There has been nothing but trouble</i>
<i>since Prince I-AN entered your life.</i>

01:09:59.870 --> 01:10:01.163 line:80%
Let's call off this marriage.

01:10:04.166 --> 01:10:05.751 line:80%
What the hell are you doing?

01:10:06.335 --> 01:10:07.753 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>This is how you protect someone.</i>

01:10:08.963 --> 01:10:10.840 line:20%
Just marry me instead.

01:10:10.923 --> 01:10:12.842 line:20%
Are you trying to protect that maiden?

01:10:12.925 --> 01:10:13.926 line:20%
SAY IT TO MY FACE

01:10:14.010 --> 01:10:15.428 line:20%
You never learned to bend.

01:10:15.511 --> 01:10:16.971 line:20%
Do not bend to their will.

01:10:17.054 --> 01:10:19.890 line:20%
<i>Do not back away and do not compromise.</i>

01:10:21.475 --> 01:10:23.102 line:20%
<i>That's how you and I both</i>

01:10:23.185 --> 01:10:24.603 line:20%
<i>get what we want.</i>

01:10:30.776 --> 01:10:32.153 line:20%
EPILOGUE

01:10:32.236 --> 01:10:34.739 line:20%
-Kiss!
-No! Stop!

01:10:34.822 --> 01:10:37.283 line:20%
-Kiss!
-No! They can't kiss!

01:10:37.366 --> 01:10:39.869 line:20%
-Kiss!
-No kiss! Where's the camera?

01:10:39.952 --> 01:10:41.245 line:20%
Should we speed things up?

01:10:42.830 --> 01:10:43.873 line:20%
Be sexy

01:10:44.957 --> 01:10:46.042 line:20%
and shameless?

01:10:48.753 --> 01:10:54.175 line:20%
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

01:10:54.258 --> 01:11:00.723 line:20%
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

01:11:00.806 --> 01:11:07.021 line:20%
MUST UPHOLD HIS DECORUM

01:11:07.104 --> 01:11:08.147 line:20%
Sorry, we can't.

01:11:08.689 --> 01:11:09.899 line:20%
We can't!

01:11:09.982 --> 01:11:11.275 line:20%
[mouths words] We can't kiss.

01:11:49.230 --> 01:11:51.232 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:12:01.408 --> 01:12:06.247 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN